%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%2040-year%20mortgage%20is%20the%20answer%20to%20improving%20home%20affordability%2C%20CEO%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20places%20a%20coin%20into%20a%20coin%20slot%20in%20the%20roof%20of%20a%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c6b1815da406397bf7d8bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Chelsea%20Jia%20Feng%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%2040-year%20mortgage%20could%20make%20homeownership%20attainable%20for%20more%20Americans%2C%20a%20CEO%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBryant%20argues%20that%20extending%20mortgage%20terms%20would%20address%20the%20affordability%20crisis%20amid%20high%20rates%20and%20record%20prices.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%2040-year%20mortgage%20aligns%20with%20modern%20life%20expectancy%20and%20could%20boost%20economic%20stability%2C%20Bryant%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOwning%20a%20home%20in%20America%20feels%20like%20a%20dream%20for%20many%2C%20but%20it%20could%20become%20a%20reality%20if%20the%20government%20begins%20offering%20a%2040-year%20mortgage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F08%2F20%2Fop-ed-the-case-for-a-40-year-mortgage.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20recent%20CNBC%20op-ed%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20John%20Hope%20Bryant%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Operation%20Hope%2C%20a%20financial%20literacy%20non-profit%2C%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBryant%20wrote%20that%20amid%20an%20extended%20period%20of%20elevated%20mortgage%20rates%20and%20record%20home%20prices%2C%20extending%20the%20duration%20of%20the%20typical%2030-year%20fixed%20mortgage%20by%20a%20decade%20would%20open%20the%20door%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20prospective%20home%20buyers%20who%20have%20been%20boxed%20out%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fhousing-affordability%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20ongoing%20affordability%20crisis.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20propose%20a%20bold%20new%20approach%3A%20a%2040-year%20mortgage%20using%20the%20Federal%20Home%20Loan%20Bank%20(FHLB)%20system%20as%20the%20framework%2C%20with%20federal%20subsidies%20for%20first-time%20homebuyers%20who%20complete%20financial%20literacy%20training%2C%26quot%3B%20Bryant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20proposal%20would%20drive%20economic%20growth%20as%20more%20people%20buy%20homes%20and%20spend%20money%20on%20furniture%2C%20appliances%2C%20renovation%20projects%2C%20and%20home%20services%2C%20Bryant%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20making%20homeownership%20attainable%20for%20more%20Americans%2C%20we%20lay%20the%20foundation%20for%20a%20more%20resilient%20economy.%20Homeowners%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20save%2C%20invest%20in%20their%20communities%2C%20and%20contribute%20to%20economic%20stability%2C%26quot%3B%20Bryant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%2040-year%20mortgage%20would%20also%20better%20align%20with%20today's%20life%20expectancy%20rate%2C%20according%20to%20the%20op-ed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20margin%20in%20the%2030-year%20mortgage%20term%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20born%20during%20the%20Great%20Depression%20when%20life%20expectancy%20was%20also%20around%2060%20years.%20Today%2C%20with%20life%20expectancy%20nearing%2080%20years%2C%20a%2040-year%20term%20aligns%20better%20with%20modern%20realities%2C%26quot%3B%20Bryant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20difference%20in%20a%20monthly%20mortgage%20payment%20for%20a%2040-year%20loan%20compared%20to%20a%2030-year%20loan%20is%207%25%20at%20current%20interest%20rates%2C%20according%20to%20Business%20Insider%20calculations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPutting%2020%25%20down%20on%20a%20median%20US%20home%20price%20of%20%24412%2C000%20would%20result%20in%20a%20monthly%20payment%20of%20%241%2C930%20for%20a%2040-year%20mortgage%2C%20compared%20to%20%242%2C083%20per%20month%20for%20a%2030-year%20mortgage.%20The%20calculation%20excludes%20tax%20and%20insurance%20payments%20and%20uses%20the%20current%2030-year%20fixed%20mortgage%20rate%20of%206.50%25%20in%20both%20calculations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20difference%20in%20monthly%20payments%20would%20be%20even%20more%20pronounced%20if%20mortgage%20rates%20decline%20from%20current%20levels%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-interest-rate-cut-outlook-september-labor-nonfarm-retail-consumer-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20prepares%20to%20cut%20rates%20in%20September.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drawback%20of%20a%2040-year%20mortgage%20compared%20to%20a%2030-year%20mortgage%20is%20that%20even%20with%20a%20lower%20monthly%20payment%2C%20it%20would%20lead%20to%20more%20money%20being%20spend%20on%20interest%20over%20the%20lifetime%20of%20the%20loan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Bryan%20sees%20that%20drawback%20as%20a%20small%20one%20if%20it%20means%20more%20people%20could%20buy%20homes%20and%20start%20building%20equity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20many%2C%20the%20alternative%20is%20indefinite%20renting%2C%20which%20builds%20no%20equity%20and%20leaves%20families%20vulnerable%20to%20rising%20rents%20and%20economic%20displacement.%20A%2040-year%20mortgage%20allows%20more%20people%20to%20begin%20building%20equity%20sooner%2C%20offering%20a%20pathway%20to%20long-term%20financial%20stability%20and%20sustained%20human%20dignity%20%E2%80%94%20a%20key%20element%20of%20the%20American%20Dream%2C%26quot%3B%20Bryant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBryant%20said%20a%20longer-term%20mortgage%20loan%20would%20help%20close%20the%20wealth%20inequality%20gap%20in%20the%20country%20and%20could%20even%20prevent%20a%20financial%20calamity%20like%20the%202008%20Great%20Financial%20Crisis%20from%20happening%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20approach%20aligns%20with%20broader%20goals%20of%20economic%20sustainability.%20By%20focusing%20on%20financial%20literacy%20and%20responsible%20lending%2C%20we%20can%20avoid%20past%20pitfalls%20like%20the%202008%20housing%20crisis%2C%20building%20a%20housing%20market%20that%20is%20inclusive%2C%20stable%2C%20and%20growth-oriented%2C%26quot%3B%20Bryant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20a%2040-year%20mortgage%20would%20help%20lower%20monthly%20mortgage%20payments%20compared%20to%20a%2030-year%20mortgage%2C%20it%20wouldn't%20address%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-housing-market-home-prices-outlook-record-high-rates-sunbelt-2024-8%23%3A~%3Atext%3DUS%2520Housing%2520Market%2520to%2520Hit%2CTrillion%2520Valuation%253A%2520Redfin%2520%252D%2520Business%2520Insider%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsistent%20surge%20in%20home%20prices%20to%20record%20levels%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20it%20could%20even%20exacerbate%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20homes%20need%20to%20be%20built%20to%20fix%20the%20key%20issue%20of%20soaring%20home%20prices%2C%20as%20Americans%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-housing-affordability-home-shortage-market-construction-population-cities-zillow-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtinue%20to%20grapple%20with%20a%20shortage%20of%20available%20homes%20to%20buy.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F40-year-mortgage-answer-to-improving-home-affordability-rates-ceo-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724333220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c6b19e5da406397bf7d8c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F40-year-mortgage-answer-to-improving-home-affordability-rates-ceo-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBy%20making%20homeownership%20attainable%20for%20more%20Americans%2C%20we%20lay%20the%20foundation%20for%20a%20more%20resilient%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20Hope%20Bryant%20wrote%20this%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F40-year-mortgage-answer-to-improving-home-affordability-rates-ceo-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fast%20food%20has%20a%20Gen%20Z%20problem%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224216%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20ordering%20out%20a%20fast-food%20restaurant%20on%20a%20digital%20screen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c10f7543bb77284ba38db8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222811%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWoman%20ordering%20from%20fast-food%20restaurant%20on%20a%20digital%20screen.%3Cp%3Esimonapilolla%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGen%20Z%20doesn't%20see%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-reporter-orders-mcdonalds-chick-fil-burger-king-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efast%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20same%20way%20as%20older%20generations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDiners%20in%20the%20age%20group%20are%20less%20likely%20to%20say%20that%20fast%20food%20is%20a%20good%20deal%2C%20Morning%20Consult%20found.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFor%20chains%20like%20McDonald's%2C%20the%20solution%20isn't%20as%20simple%20as%20%245%20meal%20deals%2C%20an%20analyst%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20youngest%20consumers%20aren't%20the%20biggest%20fans%20of%20fast%20food%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20a%20problem%20for%20big%20chains%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-big-arch-bigger-burger-fast-food-canada-portugal-menu-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMcDonald's%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGen%20Z%20diners%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-other-fast-food-still-seen-as-pricey-despite-deals-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurveyed%20by%20Morning%20Consult%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20less%20likely%20to%20say%20that%20they%20thought%20fast-food%20chains%20were%20a%20good%20value%20than%20all%20of%20the%20older%20generations.%20Morning%20Consult%20collected%20the%20data%20in%20monthly%20polls%20over%20the%20course%20of%20this%20year%20and%20also%20broke%20results%20down%20for%20other%20generations%2C%20including%20Millenials%2C%20Gen%20X%2C%20and%20Baby%20Boomers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWinning%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-women-personal-finance-investing-stocks-wealth-savings-retirement-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGen%20Z%3C%2Fa%3E%20diners%20is%20key%2C%20said%20Lindsey%20Roeschke%2C%20a%20travel%20%26amp%3B%20hospitality%20analyst%20for%20Morning%20Consult%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20Gen%20Z%20consumers%20are%20teens%20or%20young%20adults%20just%20deciding%20what%20their%20favorite%20brands%20and%20dining%20habits%20look%20like%2C%20Roeschke%20said.%20Older%20members%20of%20the%20generation%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20are%20becoming%20parents%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20most%20common%20fast-food%20consumers%2C%20given%20that%20they're%20often%20looking%20for%20a%20quick%2C%20easy%20meal%20for%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20don't%20reach%20them%20and%20connect%20with%20them%20right%20now%2C%20there's%20a%20chance%20that%20they'll%20alienate%20them%20as%20they%20become%20even%20more%20important%20of%20a%20target%2C%26quot%3B%20Roeschke%20said%20of%20the%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20majorities%20of%20each%20age%20group%20said%20that%20they%20found%20fast%20food%20a%20good%20value%2C%20there%20were%20differences%20between%20them.%20In%20July%2C%20the%20most%20recent%20month%20in%20the%20survey%2C%20Gen%20X%20diners%20said%20that%20fast%20food%20was%20a%20good%20value%20by%2048%20percentage%20points.%20For%20Gen%20Z%20diners%2C%20the%20margin%20was%20smaller%20at%2034%20percentage%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221516%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20line%20graphs%20from%20Morning%20Consult%20show%20that%20Gen%20Z%20diners%20are%20less%20likely%20than%20older%20generations%20to%20say%20that%20fast%20food%20is%20a%20good%20value%20or%20purchase%20fast%20food.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c638095da406397bf7bee4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22998%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECharts%20show%20that%20Gen%20Z%20diners%20are%20less%20likely%20to%20believe%20that%20fast%20food%20is%20a%20good%20value%20and%20purchase%20it%20compared%20to%20older%20groups%20of%20consumers.%3Cp%3EMorning%20Consult%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20Baby%20Boomers%2C%20Gen%20Z%20diners%20were%20also%20less%20likely%20than%20Millennials%20or%20members%20of%20Gen%20X%20to%20say%20that%20they%20were%20likely%20to%20purchase%20fast%20food%20%E2%80%94%20a%20metric%20Morning%20Consult%20calls%20%26quot%3Bnet%20purchasing%20consideration.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20years%20of%20raising%20prices%2C%20many%20fast-food%20chains%20started%20offering%20discounts%20this%20year%2C%20including%20revamped%20value%20menus%20and%20limited-time%20meal%20deals%2C%20as%20sales%20slipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20highest-profile%20example%20so%20far%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcustomers-are-calling-mcdonalds-5-dollar-meal-deal-skimpy-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMcDonald's%20%245%20meal%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20chain%20initially%20planned%20to%20offer%20the%20meal%20for%20a%20month%20starting%20in%20late%20June%20but%20has%20since%20said%20that%20almost%20all%20of%20its%20restaurants%20will%20keep%20it%20on%20the%20menu%20through%20August.%20Burger%20King%20and%20Wendy's%20have%20also%20debuted%20their%20own%20value%20meals%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20limited-time%20deals%20have%20done%20little%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-other-fast-food-still-seen-as-pricey-despite-deals-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshift%20diners'%20perceptions%20of%20fast%20food's%20value%20for%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Morning%20Consult%20also%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20ways%20for%20fast-food%20chains%20to%20keep%20younger%20customers%20coming%20back%2C%20Roeschke%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Roeschke%2C%20Morning%20Consult's%20past%20research%20suggests%20that%20shaking%20up%20menus%20with%20new%20items%20(think%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchipotle-tiktok-food-hack-new-fajita-quesadilla-menu-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChipotle's%20TikTok-inspired%20quesadilla%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20fajita%20veggies)%20could%20draw%20in%20more%20Gen%20Z%20diners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELoyalty%20programs%20that%20give%20frequent%20orderers%20exclusive%20access%20can%20also%20appeal%20to%20Gen%20Z%20visitors%2C%20Roeschke%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20really%20value%20things%20like%20early%20access%20to%20new%20menu%20items%20and%20insider%20knowledge%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20many%20younger%20consumers%20want%20%26quot%3Bto%20be%20the%20first%20to%20know%20something%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bthe%20first%20to%20share%20something%20with%20their%20friends.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20at%20McDonald's%20or%20another%20fast-food%20restaurant%20chain%20and%20have%20a%20story%20idea%20to%20share%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabitter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eabitter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%