able-doubt-season-2-review-1236109347%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Freviews%2Freasonable-doubt-season-2-review-1236109347%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Freviews%2Freasonable-doubt-season-2-review-1236109347%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Day%201%20At%20Kolkata%20Hospital%20After%20Rape-Murder%3A%20Top%20Court%20Highlights%20Anomalies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20deep%20dived%20into%20the%20events%20at%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Hospital%20on%20Day%20One%20--%20after%20the%20discovery%20of%20the%20body%20of%20the%2031-year-old%20doctor%20who%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered.%20And%20at%20every%20step%2C%20the%20judges%20pointed%20out%20discrepancies%20and%20anomalies%20that%20were%20more%20absorbing%20than%20any%20popular%20whodunit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20particular%2C%20the%20court's%20queries%20were%20around%20three%20points%3A%20The%20huge%20time%20lag%20between%20discovery%20of%20the%20body%20and%20the%20lodging%20of%20the%20First%20Information%20Report%3B%20the%20death%20being%20called%20unnatural%20even%20after%20a%20postmortem%20examination%3B%20the%20sealing%20of%20the%20crime%20scene%20after%20more%20than%2012%20hours.%20All%20these%2C%20the%20judges%20indicated%2C%20has%20contributed%20to%20a%20picture%20of%20a%20very%20distorted%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ball%20was%20set%20rolling%20by%20the%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepresenting%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%2C%20the%20senior%20advocate%20started%20by%20picking%20holes%20in%20the%20timeline%20of%20events%20presented%20by%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government.%20He%20said%20what%20%26quot%3Bsurprised%20him%20the%20most%26quot%3B%20was%20the%20filing%20of%20the%20First%20Information%20Report%20at%2011.45%20pm%2C%20after%20the%20cremation%20of%20the%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20who%20was%20leading%20the%20three-judge%20bench%2C%20said%20what%20intrigued%20him%20was%20that%20the%20police%20filed%20a%20General%20Diary%20at%2010.10%20am%2C%20turned%20up%2C%20but%20sealed%20the%20crime%20scene%20at%2010.10%20pm.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20was%20happening%20there%20in%20all%20that%20time%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5CnOnce%20the%20state%20clarified%20the%20postmortem%20was%20finished%20by%207.10%20pm%20and%20admitted%20that%20the%20complaint%20of%20unnatural%20death%20was%20filed%20by%2011%3A30%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20JB%20Pardiwala%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWas%20it%20an%20unusual%20death%3F%20If%20so%2C%20what%20was%20the%20need%20for%20an%20autopsy%3F%20Here%20we%20can%20see%20that%20at%2011%3A30%20pm%2C%20an%20unusual%20death%20complaint%20is%20filed.%20And%20the%20FIR%20was%20filed%20after%2015%20minutes%3F%20Give%20accurate%20information%20to%20the%20court%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20state%20remained%20silent%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDo%20not%20create%20confusion%20this%20way.%20Have%20a%20responsible%20police%20officer%20here%20at%20the%20next%20hearing%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWho%20is%20the%20Assistant%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%3F%20There%20are%20doubts%20about%20his%20role%20in%20the%20investigation.%20How%20did%20he%20conduct%20such%20an%20investigation%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Manoj%20Mishra%20chimed%20in%2C%20saying%20when%20the%20postmortem%20was%20finished%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20August%209%2C%20how%20could%20the%20police%20still%20file%20a%20First%20Information%20Report%20on%20unnatural%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20state%20clarified%20that%20unnatural%20death%20was%20first%20recorded%20in%20the%20General%20Diary%20at%201.45%20pm%2C%20the%20judge%20asked%20at%20what%20time%20the%20investigation%20started.%20When%20the%20state%20responded%20that%20it%20was%20at%203.45%20pm%2C%20Justice%20Pardiwala%20ripped%20into%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20never%20seen%20such%20investigation%20in%20my%2030%20years%20of%20legal%20career%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20filed%20a%20case%20of%20unnatural%20death%20before%20autopsy%2C%20what%20was%20the%20ground%3F%20If%20you%20have%20filed%20an%20unnatural%20death%20case%20after%20the%20autopsy%2C%20why%20did%20you%20do%20so%3F%20The%20autopsy%20is%20over%20and%20you%20know%20the%20cause%20of%20death%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20recess%2C%20the%20court's%20attention%20turned%20again%20to%20the%20delay%20in%20filing%20of%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20body%20was%20recovered%20at%209%3A30%20am.%20And%20FIR%20was%20filed%20at%2011%3A30%20pm.%20FIR%20about%2014%20hours%20later!%20Why%20was%20the%20FIR%20filed%2014%20hours%20late%3F%20I%20can't%20find%20any%20reason%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20had%20earlier%20explained%20that%20a%20case%20of%20unnatural%20death%20is%20usually%20filed%20when%20there%20is%20no%20formal%20complaint.%20The%20court%20had%20said%20it%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20head%20of%20the%20institution%20in%20such%20cases%20to%20lodge%20a%20formal%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20did%20the%20Principal%20not%20come%20to%20file%20the%20FIR%3F%20Was%20anyone%20stopping%20him%3F%20Why%20was%20he%20transferred%20to%20another%20hospital%3F%20The%20court%20wants%20to%20know%20the%20reason%20for%20all%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20questioned%20again%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Principal%20Sandip%20Ghosh%20has%20been%20questioned%20by%20the%20CBI%20every%20day%20for%20a%20week.%20Officials%20said%20he%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20give%20satisfactory%20answers%20to%20their%20queries%20so%20far.%20The%20agency%20has%20filed%20a%20status%20report%20of%20their%20investigation%20to%20the%20top%20court%20today%2C%20the%20conten