ws%2Fgodrej-boyce-targets-mkt-share-boost-with-battery-powered-forklift-truck-124082201033_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Asia's%20Richest%20Village'%20Is%20In%20Gujarat.%20Reason%20Behind%20Its%20Prosperity%20Is...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGujarat%20is%20one%20of%20India's%20top%20business%20destinations.%20It%20has%20produced%20some%20of%20the%20country's%20top%20industrialists.%20But%20the%20prosperity%20isn't%20just%20restricted%20to%20cities.%20Madhapar%20in%20Kachchh%20is%20known%20as%20the%20'richest%20village%20in%20entire%20Asia'%2C%20where%20the%20economic%20prosperity%20is%20no%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResidents%20of%20the%20village%2C%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Bhuj%2C%20hold%20fixed%20deposits%20worth%20Rs%207%2C000%20crore%2C%20which%20gives%20a%20glimpse%20of%20how%20rich%20they%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhapar%20is%20inhabited%20mostly%20by%20the%20Patel%20community.%20Its%20population%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%20around%2032%2C000%2C%20up%20from%2017%2C000%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20village%20has%2017%20banks%2C%20including%20major%20public%20and%20private%20banks%20like%20the%20HDFC%20Bank%2C%20SBI%2C%20PNB%2C%20Axis%20Bank%2C%20ICICI%20Bank%2C%20and%20Union%20Bank%2C%20etc%20-%20which%20is%20rather%20unusual%20for%20one%20single%20village.%20Despite%20that%2C%20more%20banks%20are%20interested%20in%20opening%20their%20branches%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20behind%20the%20prosperity%20is%20its%20NRI%20(non-resident%20Indian)%20families%2C%20who%20deposit%20crores%20every%20year%20in%20local%20banks%20and%20post%20offices.%20The%20village%20has%20nearly%2020%2C000%20houses%2C%20but%20around%201%2C200%20families%20live%20abroad%2C%20mostly%20in%20African%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20construction%20businesses%20in%20Central%20Africa%20are%20heavily%20dominated%20by%20Gujaratis%2C%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20expatriate%20population%20in%20the%20region.%20Many%20live%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20Australia%2C%