anger%20isn't%20helped%20when%20one%20learns%20that%20even%20in%20such%20heinous%20crimes%2C%20it%20may%20take%2032%20long%20years%20to%20get%20justice%2C%20as%20in%20the%20case%20involving%20girls%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Ajmer%20in%20the%20early%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20outrage%20this%20time%20is%20different%2C%20and%20that%20gives%20us%20hope.%20It%20has%20transcended%20petty%20politics.%20The%20political%20class%20stands%20discredited.%20The%20police%20administration%20is%20frightened.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20taken%20suo%20motu%20cognisance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20good%20thing%20is%20that%20this%20time%2C%20the%20anger%20is%20against%20the%20powerful%20system%20where%20some%20predators%20shamelessly%20cross%20all%20limits%20while%20using%20power%20or%20access%20to%20it%20for%20their%20own%20benefits%2C%20both%20carnal%20or%20otherwise.%20The%20anger%20is%20now%20against%20the%20patriarchy%20that%20is%20at%20the%20root%20of%20all%20discrimination%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPatriarchy%20And%20The%20Law%20Of%20The%20Jungle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatriarchy%20is%20a%20disorder%20that%20operates%20according%20to%20the%20law%20of%20the%20jungle.%20Here%2C%20might%20is%20considered%20right.%20If%20one%20has%20power%2C%20they%20can%20do%20anything%20according%20to%20their%20own%20will%20-%20with%20their%20strength%2C%20influence%2C%20reach%2C%20by%20breaking%20the%20system%2C%20or%20by%20forcibly%20taking%20away%20others'%20rights.%20Sexual%20harassment%20is%20the%20most%20perverse%20manifestation%20of%20patriarchy%20and%20the%20jungle%20raj%20it%20represents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20paper%2C%20we%20have%20left%20behind%20the%20laws%20of%20the%20jungle%2C%20right%3F%20But%20the%20wild%20animals%20still%20roam%20the%20streets%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20Ajmer%2C%20Kochi%2C%20Bareilly%2C%20Thane%2C%20Patna%2C%20Satna%2C%20Kathua%2C%20Hathras...%20Thousands%20of%20names%20can%20be%20added%20to%20the%20list.%20There%20are%20millions%20of%20people%20who%20still%20believe%20in%20a%20false%20sense%20of%20superiority%20that%20the%20jungle%20playbook%20affords.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20time%2C%20the%20anger%20is%20against%20those%20who%20adhere%20to%20these%20principles.%20People%20have%20begun%20to%20realise%20that%20the%20jungle%20raj%20serves%20the%20interests%20of%20a%20few.%20It%20is%20a%20kind%20of%20democratic%20upsurge%20that%20may%20lead%20to%20far-reaching%20and%20sweeping%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20are%20wedded%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20know%20how%20beneficial%20it%20can%20be%20to%20maintain%20a%20safe%20environment%20for%20women.%20The%20International%20Labour%20Organization%20(ILO)%20conducted%20a%20survey%20in%202018%20and%20came%20up%20with%20some%20startling%20findings.%20Where%20companies%20struggle%20to%20increase%20profit%20margins%20by%202-3%25%2C%20it%20was%20found%20that%20increasing%20female%20representation%20on%20boards%20raises%20profit%20margins%20by%20a%20whopping%205%20to%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20other%20salient%20findings%20of%20the%20survey%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIncreasing%20female%20representation%20raises%20the%20likelihood%20of%20increased%20profits%20and%20productivity%20by%20up%20to%2063%25%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERetaining%20good%20talent%20becomes%2060%25%20easier%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20chance%20of%20innovation%20increases%20by%2059%25%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20company's%20reputation%20increases%20by%2058%25%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUnderstanding%20consumer%20behaviour%20becomes%2038%25%20easier%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20benefits%2C%20changes%20are%20woefully%20slow%20to%20come.%20Look%20at%20what%20a%20recent%20UN%20report%20says.%20Worldwide%2C%20270%20crore%20women%20do%20not%20have%20the%20rights%20to%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20jobs%20that%20men%20have.%20Among%20the%20190%20countries%20assessed%2C%2069%20have%20some%20restrictions%20on%20women%20working%20in%20all%20sectors.%20And%20in%20as%20many%20as%2043%20countries%2C%20there%20are%20no%20laws%20to%20prevent%20sexual%20harassment%20of%20women%20in%20workplaces.%20Horrible%2C%20isn't%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20UN%20report%20also%20says%20that%20worldwide%2C%20while%20only%2061%25%20of%20women%20attempt%20to%20enter%20the%20job%20market%3B%20the%20rate%20for%20men%20is%20over%2090%25.%20And%20if%20a%20woman%20becomes%20a%20mother%2C%20only%20half%20of%20them%20get%20opportunities%20to%20enter%20the%20workforce.%20Men%20face%20no%20such%20restrictions%20after%20becoming%20fathers.%20Must%20be%20the%20design%20of%20the%20same%20set%20of%20patriarchal%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Some%20Are%20Scared%20Of%20Rule%20Of%20Law%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discrimination%20is%20beyond%20comprehension%2C%20given%20the%20kind%20of%20benefits%20that%20can%20accrue%20if%20we%20do%20away%20with%20it.%20Such%20discrimination%20can%20only%20exist%20in%20a%20patriarchy-driven%20jungle%20raj.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20is%2C%20why%20has%20patriarchy%20remained%20so%20unshakeable%20for%20centuries%3F%20Clearly%2C%20it's%20the%20interests%20of%20a%20powerful%20few.%20Those%20with%20influence%20do%20not%20want%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20to%20replace%20this%20jungle%20raj.%20The%20perks%20they%20receive%20due%20to%20their%20influence%20make%20them%20fearful%20of%20losing%20them%20under%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20patriarchy%20exists%20in%20all%20of%20us%20-%20in%20men%20and%20women%20both.%20More%20in%20some%2C%20less%20in%20others.%20However%2C%20the%20rage%20across%20the%20country%20gives%20hope%20that%20its%20hold%20will%20weaken.%20It%20happened%20after%20the%20Nirbhaya%20movement%2C%20and%20even%20after%20the%20all-powerful%20MeToo%20movement%20that%20swept%20the%20world%20not%20too%20long%20ago.%20We%20all%20need%20to%20fully%20understand%20that%20the%20destruction%20of%20patriarchy%20is%20in%20everyone's%20best%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShouldn't%20we%20all%20unite%20in%20our%20quest%20to%20establish%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20a%20system%20free%20from%20any%20might-is-right%20principles%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Mayank%20Mishra%20is%20Consulting%20Editor%20and%20Vasudha%20Venugopal%20is%20Anchor%20and%20Political%20Editor%2C%20at%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724327820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fo3dvq96_kolkata_625x300_22_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmaking-women-feel-safe-makes-economic-sense-too-6393804%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20outrage%20this%20time%20is%20different%2C%20and%20that%20gives%20us%20hope.%20It%20has%20transcended%20petty%20politics.%20The%20political%20class%20stands%20discredited.%20The%20police%20administration%20is%20frightened.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20taken%20suo%20motu%20cognisance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmaking-women-feel-safe-makes-economic-sense-too-6393804%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHave%20Blood%20Relationship%20With%20People%20Of%20J%26amp%3BK%26quot%3B%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20On%20Pre-Poll%20Visit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Cndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Frahul-gandhi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%20claimed%20%26quot%3Bblood%26quot%3B%20ties%20with%20the%20people%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fj%26amp%3Bk-elections%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20declared%20restoration%20of%20statehood%20-%20J%26amp%3BK%20was%20bifurcated%20into%20two%20