Fresh%20Fire%20In%20Kolkata%20Rape-Murder%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20said%20the%20delay%20in%20filing%20the%20FIR%20in%20the%20Kolkata%20doctor's%20rape-murder%20case%20cannot%20be%20justified%20and%20again%20questioned%20the%20role%20of%20Dr%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20former%20principal%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20who%20has%20come%20under%20the%20lens%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20West%20Bengal%20government%20counsel%20Kapil%20Sibal's%20submission%20that%20Kolkata%20Police%20followed%20the%20procedure%20to%20a%20tee%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BProcedure%20is%20a%20separate%20issue%2C%20but%20the%20point%20remains.%20What%20is%20the%20reason%20the%20FIR%20is%20lodged%20almost%2014%20hours%20after%20the%20discovery%20of%20the%20(body).%20The%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20that%20the%20principal%20of%20the%20college%20should%20have%20come%20straightaway%20to%20the%20college%20and%20directed%20the%20filing%20of%20the%20FIR.%20Who%20was%20he%20in%20touch%20with%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20moment%20he%20tenders%20the%20resignation%2C%20he%20is%20appointed%20as%20principal%20of%20another%20college%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20asked.%20Mr%20Sibal%20said%20the%20state%20will%20respond%20to%20this%20matter%20separately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20and%20Kolkata%20Police%20submitted%20separate%20status%20reports%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today.%20The%20central%20agency's%20submission%20related%20to%20the%20probe%20into%20the%2031-year-old%20doctor's%20rape%20and%20murder%2C%20while%20the%20city%20police%20provided%20an%20update%20on%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20mob%20vandalism%20at%20the%20Kolkata%20hospital%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20August%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sibal%20also%20sought%20protection%20for%20the%20state%20government%20so%20that%20it%20can%20tackle%20future%20protests.%20To%20this%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20we%20protect%20the%20State%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sibal%20then%20cited%20the%20court's%20earlier%20direction%20that%20the%20state%20will%20not%20take%20coercive%20action%20on%20peaceful%20protests.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20not%20for%20a%20moment%20said%20that%20the%20requisite%20provisions%20of%20laws%20should%20not%20be%20complied%20with.%20What%20we%20meant%20was%20stop%20arresting%20people%20who%20are...%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20clarified%20that%20that%20while%20the%20court%20had%20permitted%20peaceful%20protests%2C%20it%20should%20not%20be%20misconstrued%20to%20mean%20that%20State%20cannot%20lawfully%20use%20its%20power.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20we%20categorically%20reaffirm%20that%20peaceful%20protests%20shall%20not%20be%20disturbed%20and%20disrupted%20and%20the%20State%20shall%20not%20take%20any%20action%20against%20those%20peacefully%20protesting%20against%20the%20incident%20which%20took%20place%20in%20RG%20Kar%20Hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20also%20comprising%20Justice%20JB%20Pardiwala%20and%20Justice%20Manoj%20Misra%2C%20posted%20the%20next%20hearing%20for%20September%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20is%20hearing%20a%20bench%20of%20petitions%20relating%20to%20the%20chilling%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20doctor%20at%20the%20state-run%20hospital.%20The%20victim%2C%20a%20postgraduate%20trainee%20doctor%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20the%20seminar%20hall%20of%20the%20hospital%20on%20August%209.%20Medical%20examination%20confirmed%20rape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKolkata%20Police%20arrested%20an%20accused%2C%20a%20civic%20volunteer%20named%20Sanjoy%20Roy%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20incident.%20However%2C%20days%20later%2C%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20transferred%20the%20case%20to%20the%20CBI%2C%20noting%20no%20significant%20progress%20in%20the%20ci