ion%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20extend%20our%20sincere%20appreciation%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20taking%20cognisance%20of%20the%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20incident%20and%20addressing%20the%20broader%20issue%20of%20safety%20and%20security%20for%20healthcare%20workers%20across%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20doctors'%20body%20said%20in%20its%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RDA%20also%20noted%20that%20no%20punitive%20action%20would%20be%20taken%20against%20protesting%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20advocate%20for%20the%20rights%20and%20safety%20of%20healthcare%20workers%20through%20engagement%20with%20various%20authorities%2C%20ministries...%26quot%3B%20the%20RDA%20also%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fplease-trust-us-resume-work-supreme-court-to-doctors-protesting-kolkata-rape-murder-6377824%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPlease%20Trust%20Us%2C%20Resume%20Work%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20To%20Doctors%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%20the%20court%20told%20doctors%20abstaining%20from%20work%20could%20affect%20people%20in%20need%20of%20medical%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20earnestly%20appeal%20to%20all%20doctors...%20we%20are%20here%20to%20ensure%20their%20safety%20and%20protection.%20Please%20trust%20us%2C%20that%20is%20why%20we%20have%20not%20left%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20(Calcutta)%20High%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20appealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20health%20professionals%20return%20to%20work%20and%2C%20once%20they%20return%2C%20the%20court%20will%20prevail%20on%20authorities%20to%20not%20take%20adverse%20action.%20How%20can%20public%20health%20infrastructure%20function%20if%20doctors%20don't%20return%20to%20work%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%