und%20out%20they%20were%20building%20an%20international%20airport%20in%20Tulum%20and%20a%20train%20that%20goes%20from%20Tulum%20to%20Canc%C3%BAn%20in%2030%20minutes%20when%20usually%20it's%20a%20two-and-a-half-hour%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225f82370c-e70c-47f6-8ddd-bf24e56cb6ad%5C%22%3EWe%20found%20a%20local%20realtor%20on%20our%202nd%20visit%20to%20Tulum%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20our%20second%20vacation%20in%202021%2C%20we%20began%20to%20think%20about%20buying%20a%20house%20in%20Tulum.%20Toward%20the%20end%20of%20the%20trip%2C%20we%20started%20looking%20at%20realtors%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20was%20coming%20to%20Tulum%2C%20and%20we%20saw%20an%20economic%20opportunity%20to%20build%20our%20holiday%20home%20there%20cheaply%20and%20to%20be%20able%20to%20rent%20it%20out%20for%20a%20high%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20cost%20about%20%24350%2C000%2C%20which%20we%20paid%20for%20using%20our%20savings%20from%20years%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20house%20in%20Tulum%20with%20two%20pools%20and%20minimal%20design%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c7041d43b5e59d16b42f47%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20loved%20being%20able%20to%20customize%20the%20house.%20%3Cp%3EConie%20Suarez%20Bravo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20found%20a%20local%20realtor%20with%20good%20reviews%20and%20met%20up%20with%20him%20while%20still%20on%20our%20trip.%20He%20took%20us%20to%20several%20developments%20being%20built%20or%20selling%20their%20final%20units.%20We%20liked%20the%20idea%20of%20building%20something%20from%20scratch%20so%20we%20could%20add%20customizations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20realtor%20also%20showed%20us%20a%20website%20where%20developers%20can%20post%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20developer%20was%20building%20four%20homes%2C%20and%20he%20was%20flexible%20about%20customizing%20the%20building%2C%20which%20appealed%20to%20us.%20We%20showed%20him%20to%20the%20realtor%2C%20who%20validated%20that%20the%20builder%20was%20established%20in%20Tulum%20and%20the%20project%20was%20legitimate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2204a0be6f-7133-461b-b90f-837d4cc73bb1%5C%22%3EWe%20loved%20being%20able%20to%20customize%20our%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20developer%20had%20a%20plot%20of%20land%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftulumrealestate.org%2Farea%2Fregion-15%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERegion%2015%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20neighborhood%20between%20downtown%20and%20the%20beach%20zone%20%E2%80%94%20and%20had%20already%20carved%20out%20what%20size%20of%20home%20would%20be%20on%20each%20plot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20four%20houses%2C%20and%20the%20house%20design%20was%20based%20on%20square%20footage.%20It%20would%20be%20a%202%2C600-square-foot%20home%20with%20three%20stories%2C%20three%20bedrooms%2C%20and%20two%20pools.%20He%20already%20had%20an%20initial%20design%2C%20and%20we%20just%20heavily%20customized%20the%20house%20to%20fit%20what%20we%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20an%20infinity-type%20pool%20because%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20Instagrammable.%20I%20also%20wanted%20arches%20and%20big%20windows.%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20design%20background%3B%20we%20did%20it%20all%20through%20Google%20Slides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bird's%20eye%20view%20of%20Tulum%20house%20with%20two%20pools.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c7041d1aa2ac29ee333295%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222700%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPinlac%20wanted%20an%20infinity%20pool%20to%20create%20Instagramable%20moments.%20%3Cp%3EConie%20Suarez%20Bravo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20it%20would%20take%20a%20year%2C%20and%20it%20ended%20up%20taking%20about%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20back-and-forth%2C%20but%20overall%2C%20it%20was%20a%20fairly%20smooth%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20visited%20twice%20while%20it%20was%20being%20built%20to%20check%20the%20progress.%20As%20both%20self-employed%20business%20owners%2C%20it%20was%20easy%20for%20us%20to%20travel%20and%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2247b5037b-b53c-4a38-90b7-6e68d226801c%5C%22%3EPros%20and%20cons%20of%20building%20a%20house%20in%20Tulum%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20got%20into%20the%20Tulum%20market%20early.%20It%20hasn't%20fully%20developed%20yet%2C%20so%20there%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20unofficial%20extras%20with%20the%20builders.%20For%20example%2C%20they%20added%20a%20custom%20bathtub%2C%20made%20the%20pool%20bigger%2C%20and%20made%20the%20windows%20a%20lot%20bigger%2C%20all%20without%20extra%20fees.%20I%20think%20when%20people%20are%20just%20starting%20their%20business%20like%20these%20developers%20are%2C%20they're%20loose%20in%20that%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Living%20room%20with%20cream%20furnishing%20in%20Tulum%20vacation%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c7041c1aa2ac29ee333292%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPinlac%20said%20the%20local%20developers%20added%20larger%20windows%20without%20charging%20more.%3Cp%3EConie%20Suarez%20Bravo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bathroom%20of%20Tulum%20vacation%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c7041c1aa2ac29ee333291%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPerks%20like%20a%20custom%20bathtub%20were%20added%20as%20free%20extras%2C%20according%20to%20Pinlac.%20%3Cp%3EConie%20Suarez%20Bravo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20language%20barrier%20was%20stressful.%20My%20husband%20speaks%20Spanish%2C%20which%20made%20it%20easier%2C%20but%20he%20even%20struggled%20to%20understand%20what%20the%20developers%20told%20us.%20Luckily%2C%20our%20realtor%20who%20was%20bilingual%20managed%20the%20communication%20and%20held%20the%20builders%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECertain%20things%20got%20lost%20in%20translation.%20For%20example%2C%20we%20picked%20a%20finish%20for%20the%20walls%20that%20they%20also%20put%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20so%20we%20had%20to%20get%20them%20to%20try%20to%20sand%20it%20down%20because%20it%20made%20the%20floor%20look%20dirty.%20But%20overall%2C%20we%20were%20super%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bedroom%20of%20Tulum%20vacation%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c7041d1aa2ac29ee333294%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPinlac%20said%20she%20knew%20she%20wanted%20to%20add%20arches%20to%20the%20house%20design.%3Cp%3EConie%20Suarez%20Bravo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20downside%20of%20building%20a%20holiday%20home%20in%20Tulum%20is%20that%20there%20is%20so%20much%20construction%20around%20it%20because%20it's%20a%20developing%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20want%20to%20Airbnb%20the%20property%20when%20we're%20not%20there%2C%20and%20we%20haven't%20been%20able%20to%20rent%20it%20out%20to%20its%20maximum%20potential.%20Airbnb%20guests%20complained%20about%20the%20noise%20and%20the%20drilling%2C%20so%20we're%20holding%20off%20on%20promoting%20it.%20Hopefully%2C%20all%20the%20building%20will%20settle%20down%20in%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20investor%20who%20owns%20a%20place%2C%20I%20want%20Tulum%20to%20get%20more%20developed%20so%20we%20can%20make%20the%20money%20back.%20I%20think%20it%20is%20growing%20pretty%20quickly.%20But%20there%20are%20still%20issues%20with%20basic%20infrastructure.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20power%20keeps%20going%20out%20across%20the%20area.%20The%20internet%20is%20a%20little%20slow.%20It's%20a%20five-minute%20drive%20from%20the%20nearest%20supermarket%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20walkable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Tulum%2C%20you%20can%20keep%20that%20rustic%20feel%20in%20the%20jungle%2C%20even%20if%20it%20is%20developed.%20But%20with%20people%20coming%20from%20Canada%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20the%20US%2C%20you%20need%20decent%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kitchen%20of%20Tulum%20vacation%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c7041d1aa2ac29ee333293%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20kitchen%20of%20the%20Tulum%20vacation%20house.%20%3Cp%3EConie%20Suarez%20Bravo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229d01f61c-683b-4be2-b90e-cc4c27518a9d%5C%22%3EIf%20you're%20building%20in%20Tulum%2C%20find%20a%20local%20realtor%20and%20support%20the%20local%20businesses%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20spoken%20to%20different%20locals%20about%20the%20developments%2C%20and%20they%20said%20they%20like%20the%20tourists%20because%20of%20the%20economic%20value%20they%20bring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20on%20the%20outside%20have%20commented%20to%20us%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20you're%20colonizing.%26quot%3B%20But%20more%20development%20and%20tourism%20helps%20the%20local%20economy.%20For%20example%2C%20restaurants%20are%20a%20lot%20busier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20lean%20on%20the%20local%20people%20to%20help%20with%20property%20management.%20The%20contractors%20and%20housekeepers%20are%20local%20people.%20We%20recommend%20local%20places%20to%20eat%20to%20Airbnb%20guests%20rather%20than%20sending%20them%20to%20the%20hotel%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222467%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pool%20and%20deck%20on%20the%20roof%20of%20Tulum%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c7041c43b5e59d16b42f46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221645%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETh