he%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition's%20statement.%20'Bullets%20will%20be%20fired'%20is%20what%20he%20said.%20Suvendu%20(Adhikari)%20has%20said.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlease%20don't%20politicise%20this%2C%20the%20law%20will%20take%20its%20course.%20We%20are%20ensuring%20that%20the%20law%20does%20take%20its%20course%20after%20a%20quick%20and%20efficient%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20comes%20amid%20a%20massive%20political%20row%20surrounding%20the%20chilling%20crime%20in%20the%20Bengal%20capital.%20Main%20Opposition%20BJP%20has%20been%20holding%20protests%20and%20targeting%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress.%20The%20Mamata%20Banerjee-led%20party%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20levelling%20false%20allegations%20to%20malign%20the%20state%20government's%20image.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20also%20comprising%20Justice%20JB%20Pardiwala%20and%20Justice%20Manoj%20Misra%2C%20said%20it%20is%20also%20concerned%20about%20the%20welfare%20and%20safety%20of%20doctors.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20just%20going%20to%20lay%20down%20guidelines%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20pass%20an%20enforceable%20direction%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%2C%20several%20lawyers%20representing%20different%20groups%20of%20doctors%20expressed%20concerns%20of%20action%20against%20them%20for%20joining%20the%20protests%20that%20demand%20justice%20for%20the%20victim%20as%20well%20as%20safer%20working%20conditions%20for%20healthcare%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20and%20medicine%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%2C%20cannot%20go%20on%20strike.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20bench%20said%20doctors%20must%20resume%20their%20duties%20because%20the%20poor%20people%20of%20the%20country%20cannot%20be%20left%20in%20the%20lurch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%20the%20proceedings%2C%20a%20lawyer%20appearing%20for%20resident%20doctors%20in%20AIIMS%20Nagpur%20said%20the%20medicos%20are%20being%20marked%20absent%20because%20they%20are%20on%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20are%20on%20duty%2C%20they%20will%20not%20be%20marked%20absent%20and%20if%20they%20are%20not%20on%20duty%2C%20then%20law%20will%20be%20followed.%20Ask%20them%20to%20first%20return%20to%20work%2C%20no%20one%20will%20take%20adverse%20action%20against%20any%20doctor.%20If%20there%20is%20difficulty%20after%20that%2C%20then%20come%20to%20us%2C%20but%20let%20them%20first%20report%20to%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20people%20wait%20for%20as%20much%20as%20two%20years%20for%20doctors'%20appointments.%20%26quot%3BPoor%20people%20cannot%20be%20left%20in%20the%20lurch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20set%20up%20a%20National%20Task%20Force%20to%20recommend%20steps%20to%20improve%20working%20conditions%20for%20healthcare%20professional%20and%20ensure%20their%20safety.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724321820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fqvqucq6g_kolkata-protest_625x300_14_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medical-college-dont-politicise-chief-justice-to-centre-bengal-in-kolkata-rape-murder-6393020%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20today%20urged%20counsels%20for%20the%20Centre%20and%20West%20Bengal%20governments%20to%20not%20politicise%20the%20Kolkata%20doctor's%20rape%20and%20murder%20case%20and%20stressed%20that%20the%20law%20is%20taking%20its%20course.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medical-college-dont-politicise-chief-justice-to-centre-bengal-in-kolkata-rape-murder-6393020%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B