en't%20Bolt%20And%20Phelps%20Banned%3F%26quot%3B%3A%20Taapsee%20Pannu%20On%20Olympics%20Gender%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAlgerian%20boxer%20Imane%20Khelif%20was%20surrounded%20by%20controversy%20in%20the%20recently-concluded%20Paris%20Olympics%202024.%20The%20pugilist%20won%20a%20gold%20medal%20in%20the%20women's%2066kg%20category%20at%20the%20Games%20but%20the%20path%20to%20the%20glory%20was%20really%20a%20tough%20one%20for%20Khelif.%20She%20saw%20questions%20being%20raised%20over%20her%20gender%20whenever%20she%20won%20a%20boxing%20bout.%20The%20criticism%20continued%20but%20Khelif%20didn't%20let%20all%20that%20impact%20her%20performance%20and%20clinched%20the%20top%20honour%20at%20the%20event%20in%20Paris.%20While%20the%20debate%20over%20her%20gender%20row%20continues%20to%20gain%20prominance%2C%20Indian%20actress%20Taapsee%20Pannu%20gave%20a%20debate-stirring%20verdict.%20While%20speaking%20about%20the%20Olympics%20gender%20row%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aninews.in%2Fnews%2Fentertainment%2Fbollywood%2Fusain-bolt-michael-phelpswhy-arent-they-banned-taapsee-pannu-on-imane-khelif-gender-row-at-paris-olympics20240821172023%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EANI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Taapsee%20said%20that%20there%20is%20no%20fault%20of%20any%20athlete%20if%20he%20or%20she%20is%20born%20with%20some%20higher%20level%20of%20testosterone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20played%20a%20role%20on%20that%20subject.%20I%20did%20a%20film%20called%20'Rashmi%20Rocket'%20which%20was%20about%20a%20female%20athlete%20being%20banned%20because%20she%20was%20detected%20with%20a%20high%20level%20of%20testosterone.%20So%2C%20I%20played%20this%20role.%20I%20mean%20we%20presented%20our%20views%20and%20that's%20why%20you%20know%20I%20think%20the%20beauty%20of%20the%20kind%20of%20films%20I%20get%20is%20sometimes%20I%20get%20my%20films%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20muddas%20(issues)%20that%20I%20personally%20believe%20in%20without%20making%20a%20statement%20outside%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20actress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Rashmi%20Rocket'%20is%20a%20movie%20about%20a%20young%20girl%20runner%20from%20a%20small%20village%20who%20becomes%20a%20national%20athlete.%20She%20wins%20accolades%20for%20the%20country%20but%20her%20life%20takes%20a%20turn%20when%20she's%20called%20in%20for%20a%20gender%20verification%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20a%20film%20that%20I%20spoke%20about%20where%20I%20played%20the%20athlete.%20And%20it%20is%20not%20in%20my%20control%20what%20my%20hormones%20are.%20It's%20not%20like%20I've%20taken%20supplements.%20It's%20not%20like%20I've%20injected%20any%20hormones.%20It's%20just%20I%20was%20born%20with%20it.%20Our%20argument%20in%20the%20film%20was%20that%20there%20are%20so%20many%20athletes%20who%20are%20born%20with%20an%20edge%20over%20others.%20Like%20Usain%20Bolt%20and%20Michael%20Phelps%2C%20all%20these%20people%20are%20also%20born%20with%20a%20certain%20biological%20edge%20over%20others.%20Why%20are%20they%20not%20banned%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20why%20only%20someone%20who%20has%20a%20higher%20level%20of%20testosterone%20is%20banned%3F%20If%20she%20has%20taken%20injections%20for%20this%20particular%20competition%2C%20then%2C%20of%20course%2C%20it%20should%20be%20illegal%20and%20she%20should%20be%20banned.%20But%20if%20she%20is%20not%2C%20then%20by%20something%20that%20is%20not%20in%20her%20control%2C%20you've%20banned%20her.%20So%20that's%20the%20character%20that%20I%20played%20in%20the%20film%20as%20well.%20So%20that%20was%20my%20statement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724319480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fr6bsdrpo_taapsee-pannu-imane-khelif-insta-taapsee-jeuxolympiques_625x300_22_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fwhy-were-usain-bolt-and-michael-phelps-not-banned-taapsee-pannus-debate-stirring-verdict-on-olympics-gender-row-6391321%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Whi