20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20and%20said%20he%20had%20been%20pronouncing%20%26quot%3BKar%26quot%3B%20as%20%26quot%3BKaar%26quot%3B%20and%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%2C%20Justice%20Hrishikesh%20Roy%2C%20had%20pointed%20out%20the%20error%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20hearing%20petitions%20related%20to%20the%20horrifying%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20doctor%20at%20the%20Kolkata%20hospital.%20When%20an%20advocate%20mentioned%20that%20she%20was%20representing%20junior%20doctors%20working%20at%20the%20state-run%20hospital%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BBy%20the%20way%2C%20Justice%20Hrishikesh%20Roy%20pointed%20out%20to%20me%20that%20you%20kept%20on%20saying%20'Kaar'%2C%20'Kaar'%2C%20it's%20'Kar'.%20I%20apologise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20was%20established%20in%201886%20as%20the%20Calcutta%20School%20of%20Medicine%20by%20Indian%20physician%20Radha%20Gobinda%20Kar.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20it%20did%20not%20have%20an%20associated%20hospital%20or%20a%20campus%20of%20its%20own.%20In%201902%2C%20the%20college%20got%20a%20building%20of%20its%20own.%20It%20was%20renamed%20Belgachia%20Medical%20College%20in%201916.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20it%20was%20renamed%20Carmichael%20Medical%20College%20in%20the%20honour%20of%20Bengal's%20Governor%20Thomas%20Gibson-Carmichael.%20After%20Independence%2C%20the%20college%20was%20named%20after%20its%20founder%20Dr%20Radha%20Gobinda%20Kar.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%20took%20over%20the%20management%20of%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state-run%20hospital%20in%20North%20Kolkata%20has%20made%20headlines%20after%20a%2031-year-old%20postgraduate%20trainee%20doctor%20on%20duty%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20the%20hospital's%20seminar%20hall%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20August%209.%20Medical%20examination%20confirmed%20sexual%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chilling%20incident%20has%20spa