0her.%20After%20a%20few%20days%2C%20the%20girl%20returned%20home%20on%20her%20own.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnShe%20was%20quiet%20on%20her%20return%20and%20when%20the%20family%20questioned%20her%2C%20she%20revealed%20her%20ordeal.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20family%20identified%20the%20accused%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20photos%20from%20his%20Instagram%20account.%20They%20then%20took%20the%20victim%20to%20the%20nearest%20police%20station%20and%20informed%20the%20police%20about%20the%20incident.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20comes%20amid%20massive%20protests%20over%20the%20alleged%20sexual%20abuse%20of%20two%20kindergarten%20girls%20by%20the%20school%20sweeper%20in%20Badlapur%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Thane%20district.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAt%20least%2017%20city%20police%20personnel%20and%20eight%20railway%20cops%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20incidents%20of%20stone-pelting%20at%20the%20railway%20station%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20Badlapur%20during%20the%20protest%20on%20Tuesday.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20school%20where%20the%20incident%20happened%20belongs%20to%20a%20close%20relative%20of%20a%20BJP%20leader%20from%20Badlapur%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724314500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Folj5u4a8_police-generic-image_625x300_18_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fmumbai-man-21-kidnaps-rapes-13-year-old-girl-they-met-on-social-media-6392160%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2013-year-old%20girl%20was%20allegedly%20raped%20by%20a%20man%20in%20Mumbai%20whom%20she%20met%20on%20social%20media%2C%20police%20said%20on%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fmumbai-man-21-kidnaps-rapes-13-year-old-girl-they-met-on-social-media-6392160%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Texas%20Gets%20A%20Landmark%20-%20A%2090-Foot-Tall%20Hanuman%20Murti%2C%20Tallest%20Outside%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2090-foot-tall%20bronze%20murti%20of%20Lord%20Hanuman%2C%20unveiled%20near%20Houston%2C%20symbolising%20%26quot%3Ba%20new%20milestone%20in%20the%20cultural%20and%20spiritual%20landscape%20of%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20become%20the%20latest%20landmark%20in%20Texas%20visible%20from%20miles%20away%2C%20and%20the%20third%20tallest%20sculpture%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Statue%20of%20Union%2C%20as%20it%20has%20been%20named%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20tallest%20statues%20in%20the%20world%20and%20holds%20several%20other%20distinctions%3A%20it%20is%20the%20tallest%20Hanuman%20murti%20outside%20India%2C%20the%20tallest%20in%20Texas%2C%20and%20the%20third%20tallest%20statue%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20surpassed%20only%20by%20the%20Statue%20of%20Liberty%20in%20New%20York%20(151%20feet)%20and%20the%20Pegasus%20and%20Dragon%20in%20Hallandale%20Beach%2C%20Florida%20(110%20feet)%2C%20the%20organisers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Statue%20of%20Union'%20Hanuman%20murti%2C%20which%20was%20unveiled%20at%20the%20Sri%20Ashtalakshmi%20Temple%20in%20Sugar%20Land%2C%20about%2035-odd%20km%20from%20here%2C%20during%20a%20grand%20Prana%20Prathishta%20Mahotsavam%20ceremony%20from%20August%2015%20to%2018%2C%20symbolises%20%26quot%3Bselflessness%2C%20devotion%2C%20and%20unity%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20organisers%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20the%20murti%20is%20named%20so%20to%20%26quot%3Bhonour%20Hanuman's%20pivotal%20role%20in%20reuniting%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20Sita.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20awe-inspiring%20structure%20is%20the%20result%20of%20the%20visionary%20efforts%20of%20His%20Holiness%20Sri%20Chinna%20Jeeyar%20Swamiji%2C%20a%20Padma%20Bhushan%20awardee%2C%20and%20a%20renowned%20Vedic%20scholar%2C%20who%20envisioned%20the%20project%20as%20a%20spiritual%20epicentre%20for%20North%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20organiser%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20festivities%20commenced%20on%20August%2015%2C%20coinciding%20with%20India's%20Independence%20Day%20and%20the%20core%20of%20the%20celebrations%20unfolded%20on%20August%2018%2C%20with%20the%20grand%20Pran%20Prathistha%20ceremony.%20%26quot%3BThe%20rituals%2C%20led%20by%20Sri%20Chinna%20Jeeyar%20Swamiji%20and%20overseen%20by%20a%20multitude%20of%20Vedic%20priests%20and%20scholars%2C%20were%20a%20powerful%20display%20of%20devotion%20and%20spirituality%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ceremony%20featured%20a%20helicopter%20showering%20flowers%20upon%20the%20murti%2C%20sprinkling%20of%20sacred%20water%2C%20and%20placing%20of%20a%2072-foot-long%20garland%20around%20Hanuman's%20neck%20amid%20thousands%20of%20devotees%20chanting%20the%20names%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20and%20Hanuman%20in%20unison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statue%20stands%20tall%20not%20only%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20Hanuman's%20indomitable%20spirit%20but%20also%20as%20a%20new%20milestone%20in%20the%20cultural%20and%20spiritual%20landscape%20of%20America%2C%20embodying%20the%20principles%20of%20devotion%2C%20strength%2C%20and%20unity%20for%20all%20who%20come%20to%20witness%20its%20grandeur%2C%20the%20organisers%20added.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724314260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fd5e7p1ck_hanuman-murti-texas-hanuman-statue-pti_625x300_22_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftexas-gets-a-new-landmark-a-90-foot-tall-hanuman-murti-tallest-outside-india-6391455%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2090-foot-tall%20bronze%20murti%20of%20Lord%20Hanuman%2C%20unveiled%20near%20Houston%2C%20symbolising%20%26quot%3Ba%20new%20milestone%20in%20the%20cultural%20and%20spiritual%20landscape%20of%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20become%20th