0were%20involved%20in%20the%20crime.%20If%20the%20sample%20does%20not%20show%20traces%20of%20other%20DNA%20apart%20from%20the%20Roy%2C%20investigators%20can%20rule%20out%20the%20involvement%20of%20multiple%20attackers%20in%20the%20case%20with%20some%20certainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20sources%20claim%20the%20DNA%20report%20should%20be%20enough%20to%20solve%20this%20case%2C%20the%20results%20of%20Sanjoy%20Roy's%20psychological%20exam%20and%20polygraphy%20test%20will%20also%20play%20an%20important%20role%20even%20though%20they%20are%20not%20admissible%20in%20court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20samples%20are%20currently%20being%20processed%20in%20the%20CBI's%20Central%20Forensic%20Science%20Laboratory%20(CFSL)%20lab.%20A%20report%20will%20be%20available%20soon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20autopsy%20of%20the%20trainee%20doctor%20was%20conducted%2C%20social%20media%20was%20flooded%20with%20posts%20claiming%20severe%20injuries%20to%20his%20body%20like%20fractured%20bones%20and%20150%20mg%20of%20semen%20which%20was%20allegedly%20found%20in%20her%20body%2C%20suggesting%20gangrape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kolkata%20Police%20have%20denied%20these%20claims.%20%26quot%3BSomeone%20said%20150%20gm%20semen%20is%20found.%20I%20don't%20know%20where%20they%20have%20found%20this%20kind%20of%20Information.%20And%20it%20is%20circulating%20in%20media%20in%20all%20kinds%20of%20forms.%20People%20are%20tempted%20to%20believe%20it%20and%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20create%20confusion%20among%20the%20people.%26quot%3B%20Kolkata%20Police%20chief%20Vineet%20Goyal%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724311260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F2fiichd_kolkata-doctor-rape-accused_625x300_12_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-dna-report-could-be-most-important-evidence-in-kolkata-rape-murder-case-6391795%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20anger%20rising%20over%2