%20%26quot%3BEven%20if%20we%20have%20differences%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20nation%2C%20we%20have%20to%20be%20united.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20our%20minds%20think%20together.%20Let%20our%20hearts%20beat%20as%20one.%20All%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20society.%20May%20this%20make%20us%20powerful%20so%20we%20can%20unite%20and%20make%20our%20nation%20proud%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhatt%20also%20urged%20America%20to%20choose%20a%20leader%20who%20believes%20in%20the%20Vedic%20concept%20of%20'Vasudhaiva%20Kutumbakam%20(the%20whole%20world%20is%20one%20family).'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20mentioned%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20one%20universal%20family.%20Truth%20is%20our%20foundation%20and%20always%20prevails.%20Lead%20us%20from%20unreal%20to%20real%2C%20from%20darkness%20to%20the%20light%2C%20and%20from%20death%20to%20immortality.%20Om%20Shanti%2C%20Shanti%2C%20Shanti.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplying%20to%20the%20prayer%20conducted%20by%20Bhatt%2C%20Ajay%20Bhutoria%2C%20Deputy%20National%20Finance%20Chair%20of%20the%20Democratic%20Party%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BRakesh%20Bhatt's%20Hindu%20prayer%20at%20the%20DNC%20today%20is%20a%20significant%20moment%2C%20showcasing%20the%20Democratic%20Party's%20commitment%20to%20inclusivity%20and%20diversity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20heartening%20to%20see%20the%20rich%20cultural%20and%20spiritual%20traditions%20of%20the%20Indian%20American%20community%20being%20honoured%20on%20such%20a%20prominent%20stage.%20This%20moment%20reflects%20the%20growing%20influence%20and%20recognition%20of%20our%20community%20within%20the%20fabric%20of%20American%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhatt%20is%20a%20Madhwa%20priest%20from%20Bengaluru%20who%20has%20trained%20in%20Rig%20Veda%20and%20Tantrasaara%20(Maadhva)%20Agama%2C%20under%20his%20guru%2C%20Pejavar%20Swamiji%20of%20Udupi%20Ashta%20Matha%2C%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20received%20his%20English%20and%20Kannada%20degrees%20from%20Osteen%20College%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20his%20Sanskrit%20degree%20from%20Jayachamarajendra%20College.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20acquire%20Vedic%20knowledge%20he%20later%20joined%20Udupi%20Ashta%20Matha%20and%20worked%20at%20the%20Badrinath%20and%20Raghavendra%20Swami%20Koil%2C%20Salem%2C%20before%20joining%20Sri%20Sri%20Vishnu%20Temple%20in%20July%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20Governor%20of%20Minnesota%20Tim%20Walz%20accepted%20his%20party's%20nomination%20for%20vice%20president%20at%20the%20Democratic%20National%20Convention%20and%20expressed%20gratitude.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724310060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Ffqbd8gjg_rakesh-bhatt_625x300_22_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchoose-leader-who-believes-in-vasudhaiva-kutumbakam-hindu-priest-to-democrats-6391264%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20the%20third%20day%20of%20the%20Democratic%20National%20Convention%20in%20Chicago%2C%20the%20chants%20of%20%26quot%3BOm%20Shanti%2C%20Shanti%26quot%3B%20echoed%20in%20the%20hall%20and%20the%20priest%20conducting%20the%20prayers%20urged%20Americans%20to%20choose%20a%20leader%20who%20believes%20in%20the%20concept%20of%20'Vasudhaiva%20Kutumbakam'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchoose-leader-who-believes-in-vasudhaiva-kutumbakam-hindu-priest-to-democrats-6391264%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Venice-Bound%20%E2%80%98Little%20Jaffna%E2%80%99%20Director%20Lawrence%20Valin%20on%20Sri%20Lankan%20Tamil%20Diaspora%20Experience%20in%20France%20and%20Turning%20Down%20Jacques%20Audiar