ing%20and%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20their%20current%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahi%20and%20Hriday%20first%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F343321%2Frahul-arepaka-harvested-robotics-hyderabad-ai-startup-laser-weeder-robot-help-farmers-earn-more%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etested%20the%20prototype%20on%20their%20grandparents%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20post%20which%20they%20tested%20it%20on%2050%20senior%20citizens%20living%20in%20old%20age%20homes.%20The%20physiotherapists%20validated%20their%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20efforts%20have%20not%20gone%20unnoticed%20%E2%80%94%20they%20qualified%20for%20the%20the%20IIT%20Tech%20Fest%2C%20IRIS%20National%20Fair%2C%20and%20the%20World%20STEM%20and%20Robotics%20Olympiad%20(WSRO)%20where%20they%20won%20the%20International%20Judges%20Choice%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20device%20will%20be%20priced%20between%20Rs%203%2C000%20and%20Rs%205%2C000%2C%20much%20lesser%20than%20current%20diagnostic%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20these%20young%20innovators%2C%20the%20project%20is%20not%20just%20about%20innovation%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20making%20a%20tangible%20difference%20in%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives.%20They%20want%20to%20prevent%20other%20grandparents%20from%20facing%20the%20issues%20as%20theirs%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Rahi%20Shah%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724252476000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-16-at-18.21.00-1724246571.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D362304%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Inspired%20by%20their%20grandmothers'%20mobility%20challenges%2C%20two%20Class%2012%20students%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20Rahi%20Shah%20and%20Hriday%20Boriawala%2C%20developed%20Walkfit%20%E2%80%94%20an%20innovative%20walking%20stick%20attachment%20tha