0for%20retail%20giants%20and%20integrating%20technology%20to%20grow%20the%20produce%20at%20affordable%20and%20a%20commercial%20scale.%20Their%20setup%2C%20Calvin%20says%2C%20costs%20Rs%205%20lakh%20and%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20grow%20500%20lettuce%20plants.%20So%20far%2C%20they%20have%20built%20farms%20for%20about%2010%20agri-entrepreneurs%20and%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Krop%20AI%20won%20the%20Karnataka%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Idea2POC%2FElevate%2F2023%20grant%20in%20the%20biotech%20sector.%20The%20startup%20is%20also%20incubated%20with%20the%20AIC%20Nitte%20incubation%20centre%20under%20the%20Startup%20India%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Calvin%20and%20Farish%20made%20a%20total%20revenue%20of%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20with%20a%2040%20percent%20gross%20profit%20on%20manufacturing%20of%20farm%20stations.%20This%20year%2C%20they%20project%20annual%20turnover%20of%20Rs%203%20crores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20our%20technology%20allows%20us%20to%20grow%20crops%20indoors%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20perfect%20weather%20conditions%20for%20better%20harvests.%20Our%20plants%20grow%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357394%2Fhydroponics-farmers-increase-income-yield-reduce-water-wastage-india-saffron-strawberries-soil-less-farming-technique%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThis%2520method%2520of%2520farming%2520%25E2%2580%2594%2520hydroponics%2Cstart%252C%2520we%2520have%2520you%2520covered.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewithout%20sun%20and%20soil%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20without%20compromising%20the%20taste.%20We%20are%20glad%20that%20within%20two%20years%20of%20time%2C%20we%20have%20not%20only%20been%20able%20to%20work%20on%20our%20patented%20technology%20but%20also%20revolutionised%20farming%20solutions%20for%20farmers.%20We%20hope%20to%20scale%20up%20the%20work%20and%20reach%20to%20small%20and%20medium%20income%20growers%20so%20that%20they%20can%20benefit%20from%20our%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Farish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Calvin%20Aranha.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724062679000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D361688%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Calvin%20Aranha%20and%20Farish%20Anfal%2C%20from%20Udupi%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20started%20Krop%20AI.%20The%20hydroponics%20startup%20integrates%20technology%20and%20automation%20to%20enhance%20crop%20quality%20and%20production.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A37%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F361688%2Fartificial-intelligence-ai-hydroponic-farming-grow-exotic-vegetables-farms-climate-change-krop-ai-udupi-startup%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RampMyCity%3A%20Paralysed%20After%20An%20Accident%2C%20Entrepreneur%20Makes%20Public%20Spaces%20Disabled-Friendly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrateek%20Khandelwal%E2%80%99s%20life%20took%20a%20major%20turn%20in%202014%20when%20he%20fell%20from%20an%20under-construction%20building.%20The%20accident%20left%20the%20IT%20engineer%20paralyzed%20from%20the%20waist%20below%20and%20in%20a%20wheelchair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Prateek%20was%20an%20energetic%20young%20professional%20with%20a%20successful%20career%20and%20an%20active%20social%20life%2C%20much%20like%20many%20others%20in%20their%20mid-20s.%20Today%2C%20he%20runs%20RampMyCity%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20works%20to%20improve%20accessibility%20for%20people%20with%20disabilities%20and%20the%20elderly%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20adapted%20to%20his%20new%20reality%20back%20then%2C%20he%20knew%20that%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20going%20to%20let%20his%20wheelchair%20stop%20him%20from%20living%20fully.%20Although%20public%20at