hebetterindia.com%2F360927%2Fsweta-mantrii-comedian-spina-bifida-disability-stand-up-comedy-wheelchair-accessibility-inclusion%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20lack%20of%20accessibility%20in%20India.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Despite%20living%20in%20a%20prestigious%20building%2C%20he%20discovered%20that%20neither%20the%20building%20itself%20nor%20public%20spaces%20like%20banks%2C%20restaurants%2C%20metro%20or%20police%20stations%2C%20theatres%20were%20accessible%20to%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20realisation%20hit%20me%20hard%2C%20making%20me%20feel%20as%20if%20I%20were%20in%20a%20permanent%20lockdown%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20with%20disabilities%20are%20forced%20to%20stay%20indoors%20because%20of%20such%20infrastructural%20barriers.%20The%20World%20Bank%20reports%20that%20about%2015%25%20of%20the%20global%20population%20has%20some%20form%20of%20disability.%20Given%20India%E2%80%99s%20population%20of%20over%201.4%20billion%2C%20this%20translates%20to%20approximately%2021%20crore%20people%20with%20disabilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20raises%20the%20question%3A%20Where%20are%20these%20individuals%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disabled%20community%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20and%20most%20marginalised%20groups%2C%20often%20unseen%20and%20confined%20to%20their%20homes.%20An%20important%20question%20to%20consider%20then%20is%20what%20the%20government%20is%20doing%20about%20accessibility.%20The%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20(RPwD)%20Act%20of%202016%20mandates%20equal%20access%20and%20universal%20design%20standards%2C%20but%20enforcement%20is%20often%20inadequate%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGovernment%20projects%20often%20feature%20substandard%20accessibility%20features%2C%20with%20ramps%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20meet%20necessary%20standards.%20There%20is%20a%20notable%20lack%20of%20action%20from%20startups%2C%20NGOs%2C%20and%20wheelchair%20advocates%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prateek%20remarks.%20To%20fill%20this%20gap%2C%20he%20created%20RampMyCity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRampMyCity%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20created%20just%20from%20my%20ideas%20alone%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prateek%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20grew%20out%20of%20my%20real-life%20experiences.%20We%20visit%20each%20location%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20ramp%20requirements%20and%20then%20devise%20a%20solution%20that%20works%20without%20disrupting%20the%20current%20setup.%20Our%20approach%20is%20always%20practical%20and%20starts%20from%20the%20bottom%20up.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-24_11zon-1723818883.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20team%20at%20RampMyCity%20visits%20each%20location%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20ramp%20requirements%20and%20then%20devise%20a%20solution%20that%20works%20without%20disrupting%20the%20current%20setup.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-24_11zon-1723818883.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-24_11zon-1723818883-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-24_11zon-1723818883-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-24_11zon-1723818883-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-24_11zon-1723818883-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361764%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20team%20at%20RampMyCity%20visits%20each%20location%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20ramp%20requirements%20and%20then%20devise%20a%20solution%20that%20works%20without%20disrupting%20the%20current%20setup.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%20began%20with%20a%20campaign%20to%20persuade%20restaurants%20to%20install%20ramps%2C%20aiming%20to%20change%20the%20view%20of%20accessibility%20from%20a%20charity%20issue%20to%20a%20popular%20cause.%20Its%20first%20product%20was%20a%20simple%2C%20attention-grabbing%20ramp%20designed%20to%20make%20accessibility%20more%20visible%20and%20mainstream%20and%20promote%20it%20in%20popular%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20challenge%20for%20Prateek%20was%20the%20lack%20of%20awareness%20about%20the%20need%20for%20ramps%2C%20making%20it%20tough%20to%20attract%20sponsors.%20%E2%80%9CBeing%20convincing%20is%20crucial%20when%20the%20need%20isn%E2%80%99t%20clear%20to%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRamps%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20any%20cement%20or%20brickwork.%20We%20decided%20to%20manufacture%20steel%20and%20aluminium%20ramps%20in%20our%20workshop%2C%20which%20can%20be%20quickly%20installed%20at%20any%20location%20with%20no%20downtime%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20This%20makes%20it%20a%20simple%20and%20efficient%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20RampMyCity%20focused%20on%20eateries%20because%20they%20attract%20a%20lot%20of%20people.%20Between%202018%20and%202020%2C%20it%20had%20set%20up%20ramps%20at%2060%20locations.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20our%20work%20became%20more%20visible%2C%20we%20began%20receiving%20requests%20from%20other%20sectors%20like%20banks%2C%20schools%2C%20and%20hospitals%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prateek%2C%20adding%20that%20even%20though%20COVID-19%20slowed%20things%20down%20a%20bit%2C%20the%20team%20of%20nine%20continued%20to%20make%20progress%20and%20installed%20over%2070%20ramps%20at%20primary%20healthcare%20centres%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20Bengaluru%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20wheelchair-friendly%20cities%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20ramped%20Church%20Street%2C%20over%20100%20restaurants%2C%2050%2B%20police%20stations%2C%20malls%2C%20and%20ATMs%2C%20making%20it%20one%20of%20the%20most%20wheelchair-friendly%20cities%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20our%20team%20is%20small%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20constantly%20working%20in%20the%20field.%20Installing%20a%20ramp%20isn%E2%80%99t%20as%20simple%20as%20it%20sounds%3B%20it%20requires%20several%20rounds%20of%20audits%20and%20surveys%20due%20to%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20unorganised%20growth%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reveals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20laws%20have%20defined%20ramp%20standards%2C%20the%20existing%20infrastructure%20often%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20meet%20these%20standards%20due%20to%20space%20constraints%20and%20obstacles%20like%20parking%20and%20drainage.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20conduct%20a%20technical%20audit%20to%20determine%20the%20best%20type%20of%20ramp%20for%20each%20location%2C%20ensuring%20that%20every%20ramp%20is%20customised%20to%20fit%20the%20site%E2%80%99s%20needs%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prateek%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ipsita%20Sarkar%2C%20who%20has%20known%20Prateek%20since%20college%20and%20has%20worked%20with%20RampMyCity%20since%202018%2C%20the%20key%20to%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20success%20is%20Prateek%E2%80%99s%20drive%20to%20motivate%20himself%20and%20those%20around%20him.%20She%20describes%20how%20they%20started%20by%20inviting%20wheelchair%20users%20to%20events%20to%20help%20them%20break%20out%20of%20their%20shells.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20turning%20point%20for%20Prateek%20came%20in%202022%20when%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Tejasvi%20Surya%20took%20notice%20of%20his%20work%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20install%20ramps%20at%2010%20prominent%20government%20buildings%20in%20Bengaluru.%20The%20startup%20successfully%20installed%20ramps%20in%20a%20park%2C%20a%20hospital%2C%20and%20at%20other%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20Dunzo%20sponsoring%20the%20initiative%2C%20they%20added%2010%20ramps%20in%20just%2020%20days.%20That%20moment%20marked%20a%20new%20chapter%20for%20us%20and%20gave%20us%20the%20visibility%20we%20needed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prateek%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-23_11zon-1723819163.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20ramped%20Church%20Street%2C%20over%20100%20restaurants%2C%2050%2B%20police%20stations%2C%20malls%2C%20and%20ATMs%2C%20making%20it%20one%20of%20the%20most%20wheelchair-friendly%20cities%20in%20India.%C2%A0%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-23_11zon-1723819163.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-23_11zon-1723819163-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-23_11zon-1723819163-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-23_11zon-1723819163-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-23_11zon-1723819163-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361769%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20ramped%20Church%20Street%2C%20over%20100%20restaurants%2C%2050%2B%20police%20stations%2C%20malls%2C%20and%20ATMs%2C%20making%20it%20one%20of%20the%20most%20wheelchair-friendly%20cities%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20RampMyCity%20has%20expanded%20to%20various%20cities%2C%20including%20Delhi%2C%20Cyber%20Hub%2C%20Galleria%20Market%20in%20Goa%2C%20and%20popular%20markets%20in%20Mumbai.%20Currently%2C%20it%20is%20working%20on%20ramping%20up%20police%20stations%20and%20eateries%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERampMyCity%20handles%20everything%20%E2%80%93%20from%20ramps%20and%20railings%20to%20furniture%20and%20bathroom%20accessories%2C%20elevators%2C%20wheelchairs%2C%20and%20emergency%20evacuation%20solutions.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20team%20provides%20special%20wheelchairs%20that%20can%20navigate%20stairs%20during%20emergencies%20when%20elevators%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20used.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20sources%20these%20products%20from%20across%20India%2C%20both%20locally%20and%20centrally%2C%20to%20meet%20various%20needs.%20Through%20this%2C%20it%20has%20reinvigorated%20the%20industry%2C%20increasing%20supply%20and%20opening%20the%20market%20to%20new%20players%20focused%20on%20disability%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20been%20asked%20by%20numerous%20organisations%20to%20create%20end-to-end%20accessibility%20solutions%20for%20their%20workplaces%2C%20which%20include%20everything%20from%20accessible%20parking%20and%20entry%20routes%20to%20doors%20and%20charging%20points.%20We%20also%20address%20how%20workspaces%2C%20card-punch%20areas%2C%20washrooms%2C%20and%20canteens%20are%20all%20designed%20to%20be%20inclusive%20and%20user-friendly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20talks%20about%20how%20India%20will%20be%20developed%20by%202047%2C%20but%20we%20must%20remember%20that%20true%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F216171%2Fips-hero-west-bengal-differently-abled-friendly-police-stations-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edevelopment%20starts%20with%20accessibility%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prateek%20shares%2C%20while%20remarking%20that%20countries%20like%20Singapore%20and%20those%20in%20Europe%20are%20considered%20developed%20because%20they%20are%20accessible.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20India%20to%20reach%20that%20level%2C%20accessibility%20must%20come%20first.%20This%20is%20the%20vision%20we%20strive%20for.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETapping%20into%20the%20corporate%20market%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reality%20is%20that%20many%20people%20have%20limited%20budgets%20for%20accessibility%20features%2C%E2%80%9D%20states%20Prateek.%20Cafes%20might%20only%20spend%20a%20few%20thousand%20on%20ramps%2C%20but%20proper%20ramps%20with%20the%20right%20length%20and%20gradient%20cost%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20challenge%20for%20Prateek%20and%20his%20team%20because%20people%20wanted%20ramps%20but%20weren%E2%80%99t%20willing%20to%20pay%20for%20quality.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20needed%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20scale%20up%20quickly%2C%20aiming%20for%20thousands%20of%20ramps%20per%20year%2C%20not%20just%20dozens.%20Even%20large%20corporations%20with%20substantial%20revenues%20often%20don%E2%80%99t%20budget%20for%20true%20accessibility.%20We%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20in%20CSR%20and%20philanthropic%20funding%20to%20help%20us%20grow%20and%20meet%20our%20targets%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prateek%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%2070%25%20of%20the%20total%20Corporate%20Social%20Responsibility%20(CSR)%20spending%20from%202018%20through%202021%20went%20to%20education%2C%20healthcare%2C%20rural%20development%2C%20environmental%20sustainability%2C%20and%20poverty%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Bain%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20report.%20RampMyCity%20approached%20these%20corporations%2C%20proposing%20they%20invest%20in%20public%20accessibility%20projects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20offered%20to%20manage%20installations%20in%20public%20places%2C%20hospitals%2C%20and%20police%20stations%2C%20with%20the%20government%20providing%20the%20necessary%20permissions.%20This%20model%20has%20helped%20RampMyCity%20scale%20rapidly%2C%20shares%20Prateek%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20startup%20is%20currently%20working%20to%20tap%20into%20this%20large%20pool%20of%20CSR%20money%20to%20improve%20public%20infrastructure.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20how%20he%20stayed%20motivated%20during%20the%20early%20days%20of%20his%20startup%20while%20adjusting%20to%20life%20in%20a%20wheelchair%20and%20an%20unclear%20path%20ahead%2C%20Prateek%20says%20it%20was%20all%20about%20taking%20baby%20steps.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20are%20consistent%20in%20working%20towards%20your%20goals%2C%20there%20will%20always%20be%20a%20way%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%2C%20quoting%20his%20personal%20mantra%3A%20%3Cem%3EKismat%20ke%20bharose%20mat%20baithiye%3B%20kismat%20khud%20aapke%20bharose%20baithi%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Don%E2%80%99t%20wait%20for%20luck%2Fkismet%3B%20it%20is%20waiting%20for%20you%20to%20make%20a%20move).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20injury%20forced%20me%20to%20face%20myself.%20I%20could%20either%20become%20my%20greatest%20ally%20or%20my%20biggest%20enemy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20Years%20after%20the%20accident%2C%20when%20Prateek%20reviewed%20his%20life%2C%20his%20past%20achievements%2C%20and%20took%20note%20of%20the%20go-getting%20attitude%20he%20had%20always%20had%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20piece%20together%20his%20identity.%20This%20led%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288588%2Fbrittle-bone-disease-didnt-stop-kerala-doctor-fathima-asla-inspiration%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erenewed%20focus%20on%20his%20goals%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20facing%20similar%20struggles%2C%20his%20advice%20is%20to%20trust%20the%20process.%20%E2%80%9COver%20time%2C%20you%20will%20see%20how%20the%20bigger%20plan%20was%20made%20for%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20never%20regretted%20my%20injury%20or%20my%20life%20in%20a%20wheelchair.%20Instead%2C%20I%20see%20it%20as%20an%20amazing%20opportunity%20that%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20had%20otherwise.%20It%E2%80%99s%20allowed%20me%20to%20see%20how%20many%20people%20with%20disabilities%20can%20live%20full%2C%20normal%20lives%3B%20travel%2C%20work%2C%20and%20be%20part%20of%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20Pictures%20Courtesy%3A%20Prateek%20Khandelwal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bain.com%2Fglobalassets%2Fnoindex%2F2022%2Fbain_report_india_philanthropy_report-2022.pdf%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bain.com%2Fglobalassets%2Fnoindex%2F2022%2Fbain_report_india_philanthropy_report-2022.pdf%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Bain%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20India%20Philanthrophy%20Report%202022%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldbank.org%2Fen%2Ftopic%2Fdisability%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOne%2520billion%2520people%252C%2520or%252015%2Cexperience%2520some%2520form%2520of%2520disability.%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldbank.org%2Fen%2Ftopic%2Fdisability%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOne%2520billion%2520people%252C%2520or%252015%2Cexperience%2520some%2520form%2520of%2520disability.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Disability%20Inclusion%20%E2%80%93%20World%20Bank%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiacode.nic.in%2Fbitstream%2F123456789%2F15939%2F1%2Fthe_rights_of_persons_with_disabilities_act%252C_2016.pdf%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiacode.nic.in%2Fbitstream%2F123456789%2F15939%2F1%2Fthe_rights_of_persons_with_disabilities_act%252C_2016.pdf%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Rights%20Of%20Persons%20With%20Disabilities%20Act%2C%202016%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723821866000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-27_11zon-1723818970.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D361727%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengaluru-based%20Prateek%20Khandelwal%20was%20paralysed%20after%20an%20accident.%20As%20a%20wheelchair-user%2C%20he%20feared%20that%20he%20would%20be%20forced%20into%20a%20permanent%20lockdown.%20He%20started%20RampMyCity%2C%20a%20startup%20working%20towards%20making%20public%20places%20inclusive%20and%20disabled-friendly.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tanvi%20Dalvi%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F361727%2Fwheelchair-friendly-places-to-visit-in-bengaluru-ramp-my-city-prateek-khandelwal-access-for-disabled-people%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%202%20Friends%20Built%20Low-Cost%2C%20Eco-Toilets%20in%20a%20Rural%20Govt%20School%20in%20Just%201%20Month%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJust%20a%20while%20ago%2C%20students%20in%20the%20government%20school%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20Nellivasal%20village%20were%20forced%20to%20go%20out%20in%20the%20open%20for%20defecation.%20Without%20any%20proper%20toilet%20facility%2C%20they%20urinated%20at%20the%20corner%20of%20the%20campus%20building%20at%20night%2C%20creating%20a%20stench%20in%20the%20entire%20hostel%20block%20that%20made%20it%20unbearable%20to%20sit%20in%20the%20dining%20area%20of%20the%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocated%20in%20the%20hilly%20forest%20area%20of%20the%20Jawadhu%20Hills%20(Eastern%20Ghats)%20in%20Tirupathur%20district%2C%20the%20tribal%20village%20school%20lacked%20toilet%20facilities%2C%20owing%20to%20its%20remote%20location%20and%20financial%20constraints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20continued%20until%20architect%20Barnala%20Michael%2C%20architect-turned-documentary%20filmmaker%20Vishnupriya%2C%20and%20a%20group%20of%20like-minded%20friends%20came%20together%20to%20solve%20the%20social%20issue%20through%20collective%20effort%20and%20crowdfunding.%20Keeping%20the%20constraints%20in%20mind%2C%20they%20adopted%20an%20unconventional%20design%20approach%20with%20unique%20toilet%20units%20and%20cost-effective%20construction%20methods%20and%20techniques.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20they%20constructed%20three%20toilets%20and%20an%20open%20bath%20area%20that%20cost%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20%E2%80%94%20a%2030%20percent%20reduction%20in%20total%20cost%20compared%20to%20conventional%20construction%20methods.%20The%20technique%20allowed%20them%20to%20complete%20the%20project%20in%20just%20one%20month%20despite%20the%20limited%20financial%20and%20human%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20down%20with%20Michael%20to%20understand%20how%20they%20embarked%20on%20this%20mission%20to%20construct%20low-cost%2C%20sustainable%20toilets%20in%20the%20government%20school%20of%20Nellivasal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilet-1723867159.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vishnupriya%2C%20Barnala%20Michael%2C%20and%20a%20group%20of%20friends%20came%20together%20to%20solve%20the%20social%20issue%20through%20collective%20effort.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilet-1723867159.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilet-1723867159-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilet-1723867159-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilet-1723867159-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilet-1723867159-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361807%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVishnupriya%2C%20Barnala%20Michael%2C%20and%20a%20group%20of%20friends%20came%20together%20to%20solve%20the%20social%20issue%20through%20collective%20effort.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBy%20community%2C%20for%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20began%20when%20Vishnupriya%20came%20across%20a%20heartbreaking%20news%20report%20about%20a%20young%20girl%20who%20tragically%20lost%20her%20life%20due%20to%20health%20complications%20from%20constipation%2C%20caused%20by%20the%20absence%20of%20toilets%20in%20her%20school.%20This%20disturbing%20incident%20propelled%20her%20into%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20already%20been%20working%20on%20a%20documentary%20%E2%80%98Meel%E2%80%99%20to%20show%20solutions%20for%20waste%20management%20for%20the%20past%20seven%20years.%20So%20she%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20constructing%20low-cost%20eco-friendly%20toilets%20for%20the%20government%20school%20in%20Nellivasal%20village.%20After%20initial%20discussions%20with%20a%20group%20of%20like-minded%20people%20and%20friends%2C%20they%20approached%20Michael%20to%20devise%20a%20plan%20to%20solve%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20us%20who%20were%20part%20of%20the%20project%20come%20from%20areas%20of%20water%20scarcity.%20We%20have%20known%20the%20issues%20of%20toilet%20facilities%20and%20the%20pain%20of%20open%20defecation.%20This%20problem%20aggravates%20during%20the%20rainy%20season.%20This%20was%20a%20common%20emotional%20pain%20point%2C%20which%20motivated%20us%20to%20come%20together%20to%20solve%20this%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Michael.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20dire%20situation%20where%20children%20were%20forced%20to%20defecate%20in%20the%20open%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20proper%20facilities%2C%20struck%20a%20chord%20with%20Michael%20and%20led%20the%20team%20to%20focus%20their%20efforts%20on%20the%20government%20school%20in%20Nellivasal%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20why%20we%20chose%20to%20construct%20toilets%20in%20Nellivasal%20village%20was%20because%20of%20its%20difficult%20terrain%20where%20construction%20of%20toilets%20was%20challenging%20and%20school%20children%20were%20forced%20to%20defecate%20in%20the%20open.%20This%20could%20be%20a%20starting%20point%20and%20prove%20to%20be%20an%20example%20for%20other%20similar%20locations%2C%E2%80%9D%20Michael%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20team%20went%20to%20the%20government%20school%20in%20Nellivasal%2C%20they%20found%20a%20toilet%20was%20constructed%20on%20the%20premises%2C%20mainly%20used%20by%20the%20teachers%20and%20girls%20during%20school%20hours.%20However%2C%20Michael%20says%2C%20there%20was%20no%20toilet%20facility%20for%20hostellers.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20enquired%2C%20we%20got%20to%20know%20that%20the%20school%20had%20been%20trying%20to%20get%20funds%20for%20construction%20of%20toilets%20but%20they%20could%20not%20succeed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1723809500.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20team%20constructed%20three%20toilets%20and%20an%20open%20bath%20area%20at%20the%20school%20campus.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1723809500.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1723809500-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1723809500-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1723809500-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1723809500-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361655%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20team%20constructed%20three%20toilets%20and%20an%20open%20bath%20area%20at%20the%20school%20campus.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20sought%20permission%20from%20the%20forest%20department%20to%20construct%20low-cost%20and%20sustainable%20toilets%20for%20the%20school.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20given%20a%20month%E2%80%99s%20time.%20We%20found%20that%20mobilising%20construction%20materials%20and%20workers%20was%20difficult%20in%20the%20area.%20So%2C%20we%20needed%20to%20be%20smart%20in%20building%20toilets%20which%20will%20require%20less%20cost%2C%20time%2C%20and%20resources%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20project%20was%20entirely%20funded%20by%20volunteers%20of%20the%20Cuckoo%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20design%2C%20cost%2C%20technique%3A%20constructing%20unique%20toilets%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20preparing%20a%20rough%20design%20for%20toilets%20in%20October%202023%2C%20Michael%20and%20the%20team%20started%20constructing%20the%20toilets.%20They%20employed%20innovative%20construction%20techniques%2C%20opting%20for%20ferrocement%20structures%20to%20reduce%20costs%20and%20expedite%20the%20building%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFerrocement%20construction%20technique%20is%20a%20low-cost%20method%20that%20is%20less%20labour%20intensive.%20In%20this%2C%20reinforced%20cement%20is%20applied%20over%20a%20chicken%20metal%20mesh.%20Additionally%2C%20we%20used%20polycarbonate%20sheet%2C%20a%20translucent%20material%20that%20allows%20natural%20light%20and%20outside%20visibility%20that%20could%20enable%20students%20to%20feel%20slight%20resemblance%20with%20their%20old%20ways%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20also%20used%20a%20leech%20pit%20system%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F78181%2Fvideo-waterless-toilets-just-rural-india-needs%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DEco%2520sans%2520toilet%2520costs%2520about%2C%2527flush%2520out%2527%2520the%2520waste.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaste%20management%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20turning%20human%20waste%20into%20natural%20manure%20for%20the%20school%E2%80%99s%20garden.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20system%2C%20two%20pits%20are%20connected%20to%20the%20toilet%20and%20they%20are%20built%20such%20that%20water%20gets%20drained%20through%20its%20walls%20and%20solid%20waste%20remains%20in%20the%20pit.%20When%20one%20pit%20gets%20filled%2C%20excreta%20is%20collected%20in%20the%20next%20pit.%20Meanwhile%2C%20solid%20waste%20in%20the%20former%20turns%20into%20manure%20in%20that%20period%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20construction%20of%20toilets%20has%20been%20extremely%20convenient%20for%20school%20children%2C%20especially%20hostellers.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361657%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20construction%20of%20toilets%20has%20been%20extremely%20convenient%20for%20school%20children%2C%20especially%20hostellers.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMichael%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWater%20is%20the%20main%20medium%20for%20the%20growth%20of%20microbes.%20When%20you%20remove%20water%20from%20solid%20waste%2C%20it%20does%20not%20cause%20any%20bad%20smell.%20Pits%20that%20have%20porous%20walls%20permit%20the%20contents%20to%20seep%20into%20the%20ground.%20Sawdust%20is%20applied%20to%20arrest%20the%20bad%20smell%20and%20microbial%20growth.%20It%20is%20a%20sustainable%20and%20natural%20way%20of%20waste%20management.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20Michael%20says%20they%20have%20designed%20the%20toilets%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20draws%20the%20interest%20of%20students%20who%20were%20accustomed%20to%20open%20defecation.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20built%20toilets%20in%20oval%20round%20shapes%20and%20adorned%20with%20vibrant%20colours%20to%20attract%20the%20students%20to%20use%20the%20enclosed%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F102470%2Fcarambolim-goa-village-eco-friendly-toilets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeco-friendly%20approach%20%3C%2Fa%3Enot%20only%20addressed%20hygiene%20concerns%20but%20also%20promoted%20sustainable%20practices%20within%20the%20community.%20The%20project%20was%20completed%20by%20November%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20their%20work%20was%20immediate%20and%20profound.%20The%20newly%20constructed%20toilets%20not%20only%20provided%20essential%20facilities%20but%20also%20triggered%20a%20behavioural%20change%20among%20the%20students.%20Built%20mainly%20for%20the%20boys%E2%80%99%20hostel%20at%20the%20campus%2C%20currently%20about%2080%20rural%20students%20including%20boys%20and%20girls%20are%20using%20these%20toilets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESriram%2C%20a%20Class%2012%20student%20of%20the%20school%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%20when%20there%20were%20no%20toilets%2C%20I%20would%20face%20a%20lot%20of%20problems%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20night.%20As%20it%20is%20a%20forest%20area%2C%20I%20feared%20going%20out%20for%20urination.%20These%20new%20toilets%20have%20brought%20immense%20comfort%20to%20us.%20I%20really%20like%20the%20structure%20of%20the%20toilets%20and%20also%20the%20paintings%20made%20on%20them!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Michael%20who%20visited%20the%20school%20a%20month%20back%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20the%20toilets%20were%20functioning%20properly.%20Now%2C%20there%20is%20no%20such%20issue%20of%20bad%20smell%20on%20campus%20and%20children%20are%20leading%20a%20regular%20school%20life.%20The%20improved%20sanitation%20conditions%20enhanced%20cleanliness%2C%20punctuality%2C%20and%20overall%20well-being%20of%20the%20school%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20hope%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F95712%2Fseva-mandir-rajasthan-ecosan-toilets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeco-toilets%20%3C%2Fa%3Espreads%20to%20schools%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20where%20students%20lack%20access%20to%20toilets.%20With%20our%20example%2C%20we%20hope%20to%20inspire%20architects%2C%20engineers%2C%20school%20teachers%2C%20and%20government%20officials%20to%20provide%20dignity%20to%20our%20students%2C%20protect%20the%20environment%2C%20and%20embrace%20sustainability%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Prem%20Kumar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723818152000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilet-1723867159.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D361652%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Nellivasal%20village%2C%20students%20at%20a%20government%20school%20had%20to%20defecate%20in%20the%20open%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20proper%20toilets.%20Architect%20Barnala%20Michael%2