%3B%20I%20almost%20felt%20a%20shock%2C%20an%20electric%20current%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20my%20body%20to%20move%20for%20almost%2020%20minutes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20swimming%20for%20nearly%2011%20to%2012%20hours%2C%20the%20weather%20took%20a%20turn%20for%20the%20worse%2C%20with%20high%20tides%20and%20strong%20currents%20making%20progress%20nearly%20impossible.%20Despite%20her%20continuous%20efforts%2C%20Tanvi%20found%20herself%20stuck%20in%20place.%20The%20observer%20on%20her%20support%20boat%20cautioned%20that%20crossing%20the%20channel%20would%20be%20difficult%20under%20such%20conditions.%20This%20treacherous%20region%20of%20the%20English%20Channel%20is%20notoriously%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98swimmer%E2%80%99s%20grave%E2%80%99%20due%20to%20its%20unforgiving%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20almost%20three%20hours%2C%20Tanvi%20was%20trapped%20in%20these%20relentless%20currents%2C%20her%20resilience%20tested%20to%20the%20limit.%20The%20situation%20grew%20even%20more%20daunting%20as%20three%20of%20her%20fellow%20swimmers%20were%20forced%20to%20abandon%20their%20attempts%20due%20to%20the%20worsening%20weather.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20waves%20were%20two%20to%20three%20metres%20in%20height%20and%20pulled%20you%20back%20to%20England.%20I%20was%20trapped%20in%20this%20and%20had%20to%20swim%20an%20extra%2010%20kilometres%20to%20reach%20the%20French%20coast%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tanvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Tanvi%20pressed%20on%20and%20covered%20the%20additional%2010%20kilometres%20due%20to%20the%20bad%20weather.%20When%20the%20observer%20asked%20if%20she%20wished%20to%20continue%2C%20it%20was%20an%20emphatic%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20actually%20wanted%20to%20give%20up.%20I%20had%20vomited%20and%20had%20zero%20energy.%20It%20was%20thanks%20to%20my%20coach%E2%80%99s%20training%20that%20I%20was%20mentally%20fit%20to%20continue.%20He%20had%20told%20me%20that%20it%20is%20on%20days%20that%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20like%20training%20are%20the%20days%20that%20you%20must%20show%20up.%20He%20told%20me%20that%20when%20your%20hands%20and%20legs%20reach%20their%20breaking%20point%2C%20you%20will%20feel%20like%20giving%20up.%20But%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20give%20up!%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tanvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20boost%20her%20morale%2C%20her%20husband%20showed%20her%20a%20video%20of%20their%20children%20and%20the%20coach%20showed%20her%20the%20Indian%20flag.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20swim%20for%20my%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20businesswoman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9RsgjvuVZA%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9RsgjvuVZA%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9RsgjvuVZA%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20%40swimwithtanvi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20risk%20of%20hypothermia%2C%20where%20the%20body%20temperature%20falls%20below%2095%20Degrees%20F%2C%20which%20can%20be%20fatal.%20Tanvi%20had%20to%20swim%20fast%20to%20avoid%20this.%20She%20popped%20a%20painkiller%20and%20swam%20fast%20enough%20to%20cut%20the%20current.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20after%2017%20hours%20and%2042%20minutes%2C%20she%20reached%20the%20French%20coast%20at%20Wissant%2C%20swimming%20a%20whopping%2042%20kilometres.%20(The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F88621%2Farati-saha-first-indian-asian-woman-swim-english-channel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEnglish%20Channel%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20actually%2033%20kilometres%20long).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20biggest%20mission%20of%20my%20life.%20I%20feel%20fulfilled%20and%20extremely%20happy.%20Everyone%20knows%20me%20today%20as%20Tanvi%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20what%20else%20do%20I%20need%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kiran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Tanvi%20was%20too%20tired%20to%20celebrate%20then%2C%20today%2C%20she%20is%20incredibly%20proud%20of%20what%20she%20achieved.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20life-changing%20moment%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tanvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20her%20mother%2C%20it%20felt%20as%20though%20her%20daughter%20had%20been%20born%20again.%20To%20her%20children%2C%20she%20is%20a%20magician%2C%20someone%20for%20whom%20nothing%20is%20impossible.%20For%20everyone%20witnessing%20her%20achievements%2C%20Tanvi%20is%20a%20powerful%20example%20of%20what%20a%20person%20can%20accomplish%20when%20they%20set%20their%20mind%20to%20it.%20So%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20stopping%20you%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20Courtesy%20Tanvi%20Deore%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723816133000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-deore-1723814698.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D361675%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nas