%20Dhenu%E2%80%99%C2%A0to%20sell%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20products%20like%20milk%2C%20pickles%2C%20ice%20creams.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20his%20bold%20move%20resulted%20in%20his%20own%20business%20venture%20named%20%E2%80%98Dhanya%20Dhenu%E2%80%99%C2%A0%20which%20sells%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20dairy%20products%20such%20as%20milk%2C%20ghee%2C%20paneer%2C%20curd%2C%20%3Cem%3Emawa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20along%20with%2015%20kinds%20of%20pickles%20and%20candies%2C%20and%20at%20least%2020%20varieties%20of%20ice%20creams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20he%20has%20established%20a%20multi-crore%20empire%20despite%20staunch%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20city%20office%20to%20cowshed%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Hariom%20came%20back%20and%20broke%20the%20news%20of%20quitting%20the%20city%20job%2C%20it%20invited%20a%20lot%20of%20criticism%20from%20villagers.%20They%20started%20calling%20him%20%3Cem%3Enikamma%20%3C%2Fem%3E(useless)%20and%20%3Cem%3Epagal%20%3C%2Fem%3E(crazy).%20%E2%80%9CI%20stopped%20attending%20any%20local%20events.%20People%20would%20give%20my%20example%20to%20children%20and%20say%20that%20if%20they%20quit%20studies%2C%20they%20would%20end%20up%20like%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpset%20with%20the%20criticism%2C%20he%20built%20a%20permanent%20shelter%20and%20cowshed%2C%20adjacent%20to%20his%20home.%20There%2C%20he%20found%20solace.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20a%20pet%20cow%20with%20its%20small%20calf.%20I%20would%20play%20with%20the%20calf%20and%20they%20would%20come%20to%20me%20for%20pets.%20I%20was%20the%20most%20relaxed%20in%20their%20company%20as%20opposed%20to%20being%20around%20humans%20where%20I%20felt%20suffocated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHariom%20decided%20to%20follow%20his%20heart%E2%80%99s%20calling%20and%20ventured%20into%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2