C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20her%20postgraduate%20studies%20at%20Symbiosis%20Institute%20for%20Media%20and%20Communications%20in%20Pune%2C%20Sweta%20was%20offered%20a%20position%20at%20Blue%20Lotus%20Communications%2C%20a%20PR%20agency%20in%20Mumbai.%20Her%20parents%20were%20hesitant%20about%20her%20relocating%2C%20but%20her%20boss%20made%20a%20special%20trip%20to%20Pune%20to%20convince%20them.%20Although%20she%20moved%20to%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20travelling%20in%20monsoon%20became%20too%20tiring%2C%20prompting%20her%20to%20return%20to%20Pune%2C%20and%20she%20ultimately%20decided%20to%20quit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20moved%20to%20Mumbai%20for%20work%2C%20it%20took%20me%20two%20months%20to%20find%20a%20hostel%20with%20a%20lift%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%20It%20was%20during%20this%20period%20that%20she%20became%20resolute%20in%20her%20goal%20to%20bring%20attention%20to%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20people%20like%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUsing%20her%20voice%20to%20push%20for%20greater%20accessibility%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESweta%20shares%20that%20her%20parents%20have%20always%20motivated%20her%20to%20use%20her%20voice%20for%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20trip%20to%20Rajasthan%20in%202007%2C%20she%20was%20amazed%20to%20find%20Western-style%20toilets%20even%20at%20small%20highway%20%3Cem%3Edhabas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20When%20she%20asked%20why%2C%20the%20owners%20said%20it%20was%20for%20expats.%20She%20wondered%3A%20if%20the%20Government%20can%20be%20so%20accommodating%20to%20expats%2C%20why%20can%E2%80%99t%20they%20do%20the%20same%20for%20people%20with%20disabilities%3F%20As%20a%2020-year-old%2C%20she%20was%20infuriated.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20encouraged%20me%20to%20write%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20or%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20her%20earliest%20initiatives%20was%20a%20project%20called%20%E2%80%98Give%20So